        "An F-1 student moving to another SEVP-certified school generally goes through a SEVIS record transfer between the current school's DSO and the new school's DSO, with a transfer release date, an initial reporting requirement at the new school, and a new Form I-20.": "Arday F-1 ah oo u guuraya dugsi kale oo SEVP shahaadeysan guud ahaan wuxuu maraa u wareejinta diiwaanka SEVIS u dhaxeeyo DSO-ga dugsiga hadda iyo DSO-ga dugsiga cusub, oo leh taariikh sii-deyn u wareejin, shuruud warbixin bilaw ah dugsiga cusub, iyo Foomka I-20 cusub.",
        "An interstate move during OPT or STEM OPT often coincides with an employer change, and missed reporting can affect both SEVIS standing and the running count of unemployment days, which is tracked at the federal level rather than by the destination state.": "U guuritaanka gobol-dhaafka ah inta lagu jiro OPT ama STEM OPT inta badan waxa la falgasha isbeddelka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, warbixinta la seegay waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa labadaba xaaladda SEVIS iyo tirinta maalmaha shaqo-la'aanta socota, taas oo lagu raadiyo heerka federaalka halkii uu gobolka aad u socotid raadin lahaa.",
        "An outdated SEVIS address can interfere with notice delivery from SEVP or the program sponsor, and uncorrected records can place a SEVIS record at risk of termination, which can have downstream effects on status, work authorization, and travel.": "Cinwaanka SEVIS ee duugay wuxuu carqaladayn karaa gaarsiinta ogeysiiska ka soo socda SEVP ama kafiilka barnaamijka, diiwaanada aan la saxin waxay diiwaanka SEVIS gelin karaan khatarta joojinta, taas oo cawaaqib hoosaadyo ku yeelan karta xaaladda, oggolaanshaha shaqada, iyo safarka.",
        "Apartment or landlord pet policies": "Siyaasadaha xayawaanka guriga ee guriga la kireysto ama mulkiilaha guriga",
        "Applicant Frequently Asked Questions - California Board of Registered Nursing": "Su'aalaha Inta Badan La Iwedyiiyo Codsade - California Board of Registered Nursing",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements.": "Dib-u-dhac codsiga, diidmada, ama dib-u-qaadidda farahaha ayaa raaci karta haddii dukumentiyada aad gudbisid aanay la mid noqon qawaaniinta hadda ee guddiga gobolka aad u socotid, gaar ahaan marka laga guurayo gobol leh shuruudo kala duwan.",
        "Application delays, denials, or re-fingerprinting may follow if the documents you submit do not match the destination-state board's current rules, especially when moving from a state with different requirements. Boards of Nursing also vary in how they treat the Nurse Licensure Compact for non-citizen primary state of residency.": "Dib-u-dhac codsiga, diidmada, ama dib-u-qaadidda farahaha ayaa raaci karta haddii dukumentiyada aad gudbisid aanay la mid noqon qawaaniinta hadda ee guddiga gobolka aad u socotid, gaar ahaan marka laga guurayo gobol leh shuruudo kala duwan. Guddiyada Kalkaalisada sidoo kale way ka kala duwanaan karaan sida ay ula dhaqmaan Nurse Licensure Compact aan-muwaadinka gobolka aasaasiga ah ee degenaanshaha.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance and other tasks that rely on a state ID after a move.": "Imaanshaha aan la haynin isku-darka dukumentiyada ee uu sugayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid waxay dib u dhigi kartaa bixinta shatiga iyo waxqabadyada kale ee ku tiirsan aqoonsiga gobolka ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "Arriving without the document combination the destination-state DMV expects can delay license issuance, which then delays other tasks that rely on a state credential after a move, including rental, employer onboarding, and school registration.": "Imaanshaha aan la haynin isku-darka dukumentiyada ee uu sugayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid waxay dib u dhigi kartaa bixinta shatiga, taas oo dib u dhig karta waxqabadyada kale ee ku tiirsan aqoonsiga gobolka ka dib guuritaanka, oo ay ku jiraan kiraysiga, gelinta shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, iyo diiwaangelinta dugsiga.",
        "Arriving without the right documents can delay your license and other tasks that depend on it.": "Imaanshaha aan la haynin dukumentiyada saxda ah waxay dib u dhigi kartaa shatigaaga iyo waxqabadyada kale ee ku tiirsan.",
        "Assuming H-1B-style MSA logic for L-1 or O-1 can lead to a missed amendment when the original petition described a specific worksite or itinerary that no longer matches.": "Is-malaynta caqliga MSA ee qaab H-1B leh ee L-1 ama O-1 waxay horseedi kartaa beddel la seegay marka codsiga asalka ahi sheegay goob shaqo oo gaar ah ama jadwal aan dib u-mid ahayn.",
        "Auto insurance": "Caymiska baabuurka",
        "Auto insurance minimums and rules differ by state. Insurers may need to update your policy after a move.": "Heerarka ugu hooseeya iyo qawaaniinta caymiska baabuurka way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta. Hay'adaha caymisku waxay u baahan karaan inay cusboonaysiiyaan caymiskaaga ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "Auto-detected: %@": "Si toos ah loo aqoonsaday: %@",
