        "Background check and fingerprinting requirements": "Shuruudaha baaritaanka asalka iyo qaadidda farahaha",
        "Background check or fingerprinting requirements": "Shuruudaha baaritaanka asalka ama qaadidda farahaha",
        "Based on your selected states and purpose, here are topics to verify before moving. This checklist is not a legal conclusion.": "Iyada oo ku saleysan gobolladaada la doortay iyo ujeeddadaada, halkan waxa ku jira mowduucyo aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso ka hor guuritaanka. Liiskan hubintu ma aha gunaanad sharci.",
        "Because the J-1 sponsor (not USCIS) controls the SEVIS record and may need Department of State approval for certain changes, a move can affect program compliance differently from H-1B or F-1 scenarios.": "Sababtoo ah kafiilka J-1 (ee aan ahayn USCIS) waxa uu xakameeyaa diiwaanka SEVIS waxa uu u baahan karaa oggolaanshaha Waaxda Gobolka isbeddel gaar ah, u guuritaanku wuxuu si kala duwan u saamayn karaa u-hoggaansanaanta barnaamijka kaga duwan xaaladaha H-1B ama F-1.",
        "Beneficiary-facing CMS site on Medicare basics.": "Bogga CMS ee jeedha ka-faa'iidaystaha ee aasaaska Medicare.",
        "Board of nursing requirements, compact licenses, clinical placement.": "Shuruudaha guddiga kalkaalisada, shatiyada heshiiska, meelaynta isbitaalka.",
        "Boards of Nursing may have specific guidance about documentation for non-citizen applicants, including whether an SSN is required, whether an ITIN or attestation is accepted, how foreign education is evaluated, and how license endorsement works when moving from another state.": "Guddiyada Kalkaalisadu waxay yeelan karaan hagid gaar ah oo ku saabsan dukumentiyada codsadayaasha aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn, oo ay ku jiraan inay SSN loo baahan yahay, inay ITIN ama caddayn la aqbalayo, sida waxbarashada shisheeye loo qiimeeyo, iyo sida aqoonsiga shatigu u shaqeeyo marka laga guurayo gobol kale.",
        "Breed or species restrictions (state, local, or housing-level)": "Xayiraadaha nooca ama jinsiga (heerka gobolka, deegaanka, ama guriga)",
        "BridgeUSA J-1 Program Categories": "BridgeUSA J-1 Qaybaha Barnaamijka",
        "Build a state-to-state checklist for licenses, vehicles, housing, pets, work, school, healthcare licensure, and other rules that may change when you move.": "Samee liis hubin oo gobol-ka-gobol oo ku saabsan shatiyada, gawaarida, guryaha, xayawaanka guriga, shaqada, dugsiga, shatiga daryeelka caafimaadka, iyo qawaaniin kale oo laga yaabo inay isbeddelaan markaad guurto.",
        "Build checklist": "Samee liis hubinta",
