        "CBP I-94 Official Site": "Bogga Rasmiga ah ee CBP I-94",
        "CBP I-94 site for retrieving the most recent admission record.": "Bogga CBP I-94 oo loo isticmaalo soo helitaanka diiwaanka soo dhoweynta ugu dambeyey.",
        "CHECKLIST BUILDER": "SAMEEYAHA LIISKA HUBINTA",
        "CMS Marketplace Overview of Exchanges": "CMS Dulmar Suuqa ee Is-weydaarsiyada",
        "CMS Original Medicare (Part A and B) Eligibility and Enrollment": "CMS Original Medicare (Qaybta A iyo B) U Qalmitaanka iyo Isdiiwaangelinta",
        "CMS Press Release on Federal Medicaid and CHIP Funding Limits for Certain Noncitizens": "CMS Saxaafadda ee Xayiraadaha Maalgelinta Medicaid iyo CHIP ee Federaalka ee Aan-Muwaadiniinta-Ahayn Qaarkood",
        "CMS landing page on the federal and state marketplaces. Redirected from a cciio URL.": "Bogga aasaasiga ah ee CMS ee suuqyada federaalka iyo gobolka. Waxa laga wareejiyay URL cciio.",
        "CMS page summarizing Original Medicare eligibility, including the five-year continuous residency provision for lawfully admitted permanent residents.": "Bogga CMS oo kooba u qalmitaanka Original Medicare, oo ay ku jirto qodobka degenaansho joogto ah ee shanta sano ee deganayaasha joogto ah ee si sharci ah loo soo dhoweeyay.",
        "CMS press release on April 2026 guidance to implement statutory limits on federal Medicaid and CHIP funding for certain noncitizens, taking effect October 1, 2026, and noting the carve-out for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "Saxaafadda CMS ee hagidda Abriil 2026 si loo hirgeliyo xayiraadaha xeer ah ee maalgelinta Medicaid iyo CHIP ee federaalka ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn qaarkood, oo dhaqan-gali doonta Oktoobar 1, 2026, oo lagu xusi doono ka-saaridda carruurta iyo dadka uurka leh ee si sharci ah u degan.",
        "CPR / BLS certification": "Shahaadada CPR / BLS",
        "CROSS-STATE RELOCATION CHECKLIST": "LIISKA HUBINTA U GUURISTA GOBOL KALE",
        "CUNY tuition and fee manual chapter on residency, covering nonimmigrant visa categories that may establish New York domicile and high-school-attendance provisions.": "Cutubka manual-ka kharashka waxbarashada iyo lacagaha CUNY ee ku saabsan degenaanshaha, oo daboolaya qaybaha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah ee laga yaabo inay aasaasaan domicile New York iyo qodobada ka qaybgalka dugsiga sare.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing applicant FAQ page covering documentation, SSN, and immigration-status questions.": "Bogga FAQ ee codsade California Board of Registered Nursing oo daboolaya su'aalaha dukumentiyada, SSN, iyo xaaladda socdaalka.",
        "California Board of Registered Nursing page on international endorsement requirements, including credentials evaluation.": "Bogga California Board of Registered Nursing ee shuruudaha aqoonsiga caalamiga ah, oo ay ku jirto qiimaynta aqoonsiga.",
        "California DMV REAL ID page covering documentation for non-U.S. citizens, including how the credential expiration may track the underlying federal document.": "Bogga REAL ID ee California DMV oo daboolaya dukumentiyada aan-muwaadiniinta U.S.-ahayn, oo ay ku jirto sida dhicitaanka aqoonsigu uu uga raaci karo dukumentiga federaalka ee hoosta yaal.",
        "California FTB page on part-year and nonresident filers, including a note that California does not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "Bogga California FTB ee filerada qayb-sano ah iyo nonresident, oo ay ku jirto qoraal sheegaya in California aanay raacin marka laga reebay heshiiska canshuurta dakhliga federaalka.",
        "California Franchise Tax Board page on residency, nonresidency, and part-year status for state income tax purposes.": "Bogga California Franchise Tax Board ee degenaanshaha, aan-degenaanshaha, iyo xaaladda qayb-sano ah ee ujeeddooyinka canshuurta dakhliga gobolka.",
        "Can cause inconvenience, fees, or compliance problems if ignored.": "Waxay sababi kartaa dhibaato, kharashyo, ama dhibaatooyin u hoggaansanaan haddii la iska indhatiro.",
        "Categories": "Qaybaha",
        "Categories where rules vary substantially. Verify directly with official sources.": "Qaybaha qawaaniintu si weyn ugu kala duwan yihiin. Si toos ah uga hubi ilaha rasmiga ah.",
        "Check insurance networks, student health, and prescription transfer": "Hubi shabakadaha caymiska, caafimaadka ardayda, iyo u wareejinta dawooyinka",
        "Check pet vaccination, licensing, and housing rules": "Hubi qawaaniinta tallaalka, shatiga, iyo guryaha xayawaanka",
        "Check the destination state board of nursing requirements": "Hubi shuruudaha guddiga kalkaalisada ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Check whether a destination-state license application triggers Selective Service registration": "Hubi inay codsiga shatiga gobolka aad u socotid uu kicinayo diiwaangelinta Selective Service",
        "Check whether moving creates a state tax filing requirement": "Hubi inay guuritaanku abuuro shuruudda gudbinta canshuurta gobolka",
        "Check whether your professional license transfers": "Hubi inay shatigaaga xirfadda u wareego",
        "Checklist": "Liiska hubinta",
        "Checklist builder": "Sameeyaha liiska hubinta",
        "Choose your origin and destination state.": "Dooro gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid iyo gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "Choose your origin and destination, your purpose, and the categories that apply. MoveSafe will generate a list of topics to verify before moving.": "Dooro gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid iyo kan aad u socotid, ujeeddadaada, iyo qaybaha khusayso. MoveSafe wuxuu abuuri doonaa liis mowduucyo aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso ka hor guuritaanka.",
        "Choose your states, purpose, and categories. MoveSafe will assemble a source-linked checklist with risk badges.": "Dooro gobolladaada, ujeeddadaada, iyo qaybahaaga. MoveSafe wuxuu isu keenayaa liis hubin oo ilo ku xiran oo leh calaamado khatar.",
        "Choosing the wrong credential type at the destination-state DMV can mean reapplying later, and document expiration may shorten the validity of a REAL ID issued to non-citizens.": "Doorashada nooca aqoonsiga khaldan DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid waxay macnaheedu noqon karaa dib-u-codsasho goor dambe, dhicitaanka dukumentigu waxa uu gaaban karaa muddo-ansax ah ee REAL ID-ga loo bixiyay aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn.",
        "Clears the verified state on items currently shown.": "Nadiifiya xaaladda hubinta ee cinwaanada hadda muujinaya.",
        "Clinical placement": "Meelaynta isbitaalka",
        "Clinical sites and schools may require immunizations, drug screens, CPR/BLS, background checks, and other clearances separate from board licensure.": "Goobaha isbitaalka iyo dugsiyadu waxay u baahnaan karaan tallaal, baaritaan daroogo, CPR/BLS, baaritaan asal, iyo nadiifin kale oo gaar ka ah shatiga guddiga.",
        "Confirm clinical placement and school onboarding requirements": "Xaqiiji shuruudaha meelaynta isbitaalka iyo gelinta dugsiga",
        "Confirm required documents for a destination-state license": "Xaqiiji dukumentiyada loo baahan yahay shatiga gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Confirm school residency, insurance, and immunization rules": "Xaqiiji qawaaniinta degenaanshaha dugsiga, caymiska, iyo tallaalka",
        "Confirm your auto insurance covers the destination state": "Xaqiiji in caymiskaaga baabuurka uu daboolayo gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Continue my checklist": "Sii wad liiskayga hubinta",
        "Continuing education requirements": "Shuruudaha waxbarashada sii socota",
        "Continuity of coverage after a move depends on whether the destination state operates its own marketplace, which categories of non-citizens it considers, and whether state-funded coverage is offered to people who are not eligible for the federal marketplace.": "Sii-socoshada caymiska ka dib guuritaanka waxay ku xirantahay inay gobolka aad u socotid uu maamulayo suuqiisa, qaybaha aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee uu tixgaliyo, iyo inay caymis lacag-gobol leh loo bixiyo dadka aan u qalmin suuqa federaalka.",
        "Could not generate checklist": "Lama abuuri karin liiska hubinta",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page covering personal information updates.": "Bogga xarunta kaalmada SEVIS ee DHS Study in the States oo daboolaya cusboonaysiinada macluumaadka shakhsiga.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on F-1 SEVIS transfer mechanics.": "Bogga xarunta kaalmada SEVIS ee DHS Study in the States oo ku saabsan farsamada u wareejinta F-1 SEVIS.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVIS help hub page on STEM OPT.": "Bogga xarunta kaalmada SEVIS ee DHS Study in the States oo ku saabsan STEM OPT.",
        "DHS Study in the States SEVP Portal help page describing OPT reporting.": "Bogga kaalmada SEVP Portal ee DHS Study in the States oo qeexaya warbixinta OPT.",
        "DHS Study in the States blog post on the 10-day DSO reporting expectation.": "Qoraal-bilog DHS Study in the States oo ku saabsan rajada warbixinta DSO ee 10-maalmood.",
        "DHS Study in the States guidance for F-1 and M-1 students on reporting address changes to the designated school official within 10 days.": "Hagidda DHS Study in the States ee ardayda F-1 iyo M-1 ee warbixinta isbeddelka cinwaanka sarkaalka dugsiga ee loo magacaabay 10 maalmood gudahood.",
        "DHS Study in the States post on SEVIS address-of-record.": "Qoraalka DHS Study in the States ku saabsan cinwaanka-diiwaanka ee SEVIS.",
        "DOL FLAG (Office of Foreign Labor Certification) Portal": "Bogga DOL FLAG (Office of Foreign Labor Certification)",
        "DOL FLAG portal that handles LCA and other foreign-labor filings. The dol.gov subpages returned 403 to curl with Mozilla user-agent, consistent with anti-bot behavior on a long-standing .gov domain, so this canonical FLAG portal URL is used.": "Bogga DOL FLAG oo qabta gudbinta LCA iyo gudbinta kale ee shaqaalaha shisheeye. Bogagga hoose ee dol.gov waxay soo celiyeen 403 marka loo isticmaalo curl iyada oo loo isticmaalayo Mozilla user-agent, taas oo la mid ah dabeecadda ka-hortagga botka ee domain .gov ah, sidaas darteed URL-kan caanka ah ee FLAG ayaa la isticmaalay.",
        "Decide your residency, eligibility, or tax status": "Go'aaminta degenaanshahaaga, u qalmitaankaaga, ama xaaladdaada canshuurta",
        "Department of Homeland Security guidance for F-1 and M-1 students, and Department of State regulations for J-1 exchange visitors, generally require reporting an address change to a designated school official (DSO) or program sponsor within 10 days so the SEVIS record can be updated.": "Hagidda Waaxda Amniga Dalka ee ardayda F-1 iyo M-1, iyo qawaaniinta Waaxda Gobolka ee booqdayaasha is-weydaarsiga J-1, guud ahaan waxay u baahan yihiin in la soo sheego isbeddelka cinwaanka sarkaal dugsi oo loo magacaabay (DSO) ama kafiilka barnaamijka 10 maalmood gudahood si diiwaanka SEVIS loo cusboonaysiiyo.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA categories overview.": "Dulmar BridgeUSA Department of State oo ku saabsan qaybaha.",
        "Department of State BridgeUSA landing page for the J-1 Exchange Visitor Program.": "Bogga aasaasiga ah ee Department of State BridgeUSA ee J-1 Exchange Visitor Program.",
        "Destination state": "Gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state DMV / MVA": "DMV / MVA gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state attorney general": "Xeer-ilaaliyaha guud ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state board of nursing": "Guddiga kalkaalisada ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state department of agriculture": "Waaxda beeraha ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state department of health": "Waaxda caafimaadka ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state department of labor": "Waaxda shaqaalaha ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state professional licensing": "Shatiga xirfadda ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination state tax agency": "Hay'adda canshuurta ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination-state minimum coverage requirements": "Shuruudaha caymiska ugu hooseeya ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Destination:": "Loo socdo:",
        "Determine whether a specific act is lawful": "Go'aaminta in fal gaar ah uu raacayo sharciga iyo in kale",
        "Different agencies may apply different residency tests. The same person can be a resident for one purpose and not another.": "Hay'ado kala duwan ayaa khusayn kara tijaabooyin degenaansho oo kala duwan. Qof isku mid ah ayaa noqon kara degane ujeedo gaar ah ee ma ahan mid kale.",
        "Direct users to confirm coverage with their insurer. Do not state whether coverage applies.": "U tilmaan isticmaalayaasha inay caymiska ku xaqiijiyaan hay'adda caymiskooda. Ha sheegin in caymisku khusayo.",
        "Disclaimer. %@": "Af-celin. %@",
        "Do not assert that any group is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID rules involve both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only.": "Ha sheegin in koox kasta u qalanto ama aanay u qalmin REAL ID-da gobol gaar ah. Qawaaniinta REAL ID waxay ku lug yeeshaan heerarka ugu yar ee federaalka iyo hirgelinta gobolka oo isbeddeli kara. U isticmaal kaliya luqadda 'hubi' iyo 'waxay kala duwanaan kartaa'.",
        "Do not assert that any specific state always uses a shortened renewal cycle for a given visa category. Frame as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in gobol gaar ah uu had iyo jeer isticmaalo wareeg cusboonaysiin oo gaaban qaybta fiisaha. U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not assert that any visa category is or is not eligible for REAL ID in a given state. REAL ID involves both federal minimums and state implementation that may change. Use 'verify' and 'may vary' language only and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in qayb fiise kasta ay u qalanto ama aanay u qalmin REAL ID gobol gaar ah. REAL ID waxay ku lug yeeshaa labadaba heerarka ugu yar ee federaalka iyo hirgelinta gobolka oo isbeddeli karta. U isticmaal kaliya luqadda 'hubi' iyo 'waxay kala duwanaan kartaa' oo raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not assume": "Ha is malayn",
        "Do not assume a USPS or DMV address update satisfies the federal AR-11 step": "Ha is malayn in cusboonaysiinta cinwaanka USPS ama DMV ay buuxiso tallaabada AR-11 ee federaalka",
        "Do not assume regulated items follow the same rules across state lines": "Ha is malayn in cinwaanada la nidaamiyey ay raacaan qawaaniin isku mid ah xudduudaha gobollada dhexdooda",
        "Do not assume rules from your origin state apply. Rules vary across state, local, and federal jurisdictions. Verify directly with official sources.": "Ha is malayn in sharciyada gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid ay khusayaan. Sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunada gobolka, deegaanka, iyo federaalka. Si toos ah uga hubi ilaha rasmiga ah.",
        "Do not characterize voter registration by non-citizens using legal-conclusion or accusatory language. Use neutral framing such as 'generally not eligible' and 'may create immigration complications'. Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney. Do not give procedural advice for any specific state.": "Ha ku tilmaamin diiwaangelinta codbixinta ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn luqad gunaanad sharci ah ama eedeyn ah. U isticmaal qaabaynta dhexdhexaadka ah sida 'guud ahaan ma qalmaan' iyo 'waxay abuuri karaan dhibaatooyin socdaal'. U tilmaan akhristayaasha inay la tashadaan qareen socdaal oo shati haysta. Ha bixin talo nidaameed gobol gaar ah.",
        "Do not characterize whether any visa category can establish residency in a specific state as a determination. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha ku tilmaamin inay qayb fiise kasta uu aasaasi karo degenaansho gobol gaar ah sida go'aan. U qaab dheh qawaaniin kala saarid lagu hubinayo diiwaangeluhu dugsiga iyo hay'adda waxbarashada sare ee gobolka. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not determine residency. List factors to verify. Direct to the relevant agency or school.": "Ha go'aamin degenaanshaha. Liis ka samee arrimaha la hubinayo. U tilmaan hay'adda ama dugsiga la xiriira.",
        "Do not determine that a household 'is' or 'is not' eligible for Medicaid. Frame as items to verify with the state Medicaid agency. Use 'may apply' and 'rules differ by jurisdiction'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha go'aamin in qoys 'u qalmo' ama 'aanu u qalmin' Medicaid. U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo hay'adda Medicaid ee gobolka. U isticmaal 'waxaa laga yaabaa inay khusayso' iyo 'sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not list which states grant in-state tuition for DACA recipients. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency.": "Ha liisin gobollada bixiya kharashka waxbarashada gobol-gudaha ee DACA-hayayaasha. U qaab dheh qawaaniin kala saarid lagu hubinayo diiwaangeluhu dugsiga iyo hay'adda waxbarashada sare ee gobolka.",
        "Do not provide a public-charge determination or say that using benefits 'will' or 'will not' affect immigration. Frame as 'may interact' and recommend consulting a licensed immigration attorney. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha bixin go'aan ku saabsan culayska dadweynaha ama ha sheegin in isticmaalka manaafacaadku 'saamayn doono' ama 'aanu saamayn doonin' socdaalka. U qaab dheh 'waxay la falgalan kartaa' oo kula tali la tashashada qareen socdaal oo shati haysta. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not provide medical or transport instructions for controlled substances.": "Ha bixin tilmaamo caafimaad ama gaadiid oo loogu talagalay walxaha la nidaamiyo.",
        "Do not provide tactical instructions for transporting, possessing, hiding, storing, modifying, or avoiding enforcement for regulated items.": "Ha bixin tilmaamo qaab-fulin oo loogu talagalay gaadiidka, haysashada, qarinta, kaydinta, beddelka, ama looga gudbinta fulinta sharciga ee cinwaanada la nidaamiyey.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to official tax agency and qualified professionals.": "Ha bixin talo canshuur. U tilmaan hay'adda canshuurta rasmiga ah iyo xirfadlayaasha aqoonsan.",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to state tax agency or qualified tax professional.": "Ha bixin talo canshuur. U tilmaan hay'adda canshuurta gobolka ama xirfadle canshuur oo aqoonsan.",
        "Do not say a Board of Nursing in a particular state grants or refuses an applicant's NCLEX path. Use 'verify with the destination Board of Nursing'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in Guddiga Kalkaalisada gobol gaar ah uu siiyo ama diido jidka NCLEX ee codsade. U isticmaal 'ku hubi Guddiga Kalkaalisada ee aad u socotid'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not say a particular aid program 'is open to' or 'is closed to' DACA recipients or LPRs. Use 'verify with the state aid agency and the school financial-aid office'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in barnaamij kaalmo gaar ah 'u furan yahay' ama 'u xidhan yahay' DACA-hayayaasha ama LPR-yada. U isticmaal 'ku hubi hay'adda kaalmada gobolka iyo xafiiska kaalmada maaliyadeed ee dugsiga'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not say a person 'can' or 'cannot' enroll. Use 'verify current eligibility categories with the marketplace operator' since federal rules have changed. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin qof 'wuu' ama 'ma' isdiiwaangelin karo. U isticmaal 'ku hubi qaybaha u qalmitaanka hadda ee maamulaha suuqa' maaddaama qawaaniinta federaalku isbeddelay. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency for a given visa category or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin sida gobol gaar ah uu u qeexo degenaanshaha qaybta fiisaha ama in qof 'yahay' degane. U qaab dheh 'sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta' iyo 'ku hubi hay'adda canshuurta gobolka aad u socotid'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin sida gobol gaar ah uu u qeexo degenaanshaha ama in qof 'yahay' degane. U qaab dheh 'sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta' iyo 'ku hubi hay'adda canshuurta gobolka aad u socotid'. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license a given visa category. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in guddi gaar ah uu shatiyeeyo ama aanu shatiyaynayn qaybta fiisaha. U qaab dheh wax kasta sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo guddiga gobolka aad u socotid. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license non-citizens. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in guddi gaar ah uu shatiyeeyo ama aanu shatiyaynayn aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn. U qaab dheh wax kasta sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo guddiga gobolka aad u socotid. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Frame as a federal requirement that 'may apply' depending on age and sex, with state implementation details to verify. Use neutral language and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin in qof gaar ah ay tahay ama aanay ahayn in la diiwaangeliyo. U qaab dheh shuruud federaal oo 'laga yaabo inay khusayso' iyada oo loo eegayo da'da iyo jinsiga, iyada oo faahfaahinta hirgelinta gobolka la hubinayo. U isticmaal luqad dhexdhexaad ah oo raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Do not state whether the user is eligible for licensure. Only identify requirements to verify.": "Ha sheegin inay isticmaaluhu u qalmo shatiga. Kaliya aqoonso shuruudaha la hubinayo.",
        "Do not state which states do or do not issue licenses to a given group, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV.": "Ha sheegin gobollada bixiya ama aan bixinin shatiyada koox la bixiyay, hana liisin dukumentiyo la aqbalay oo gaar ah. U qaab dheh wax kasta sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "Do not state which states issue or do not issue licenses to a given visa category, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "Ha sheegin gobollada bixiya ama aan bixinin shatiyo qaybta fiisuhu, hana liisin dukumentiyo gaar ah oo la aqbalo. U qaab dheh wax kasta sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid. Raac liiska SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Document lists accepted by state DMVs for non-citizen license or state-ID applicants can differ from those accepted for U.S. citizens, and accepted combinations may vary by jurisdiction.": "Liisaska dukumentiyada ee ay aqbalaan DMV-yada gobolka ee codsadayaasha shati ama aqoonsi gobol ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn way ka kala duwanaan karaan kuwa loo aqbalo muwaadiniinta U.S., isku-darka la aqbalayaana way ka kala duwanaan karaan xukunka kasta.",
        "Documents for proof of identity": "Dukumentiyada caddaynta aqoonsiga",
        "Done": "La sameeyay",
        "Driver's license": "Shatiga darawalnimada",
        "Driving across one or more state lines for travel.": "Wadidda hal ama in ka badan oo xudduud gobol ah socdaal awgeed.",
        "Driving with coverage that does not meet destination-state minimums can create compliance and financial problems.": "Wadidda baabuur leh caymis aan oolin heerarka ugu hooseeya ee gobolka aad u socotid waxay abuuri kartaa dhibaatooyin u hoggaansanaan iyo dhaqaale.",
        "Drug screen requirements": "Shuruudaha baaritaanka daroogada",
        "Edit selections": "Wax ka beddel doorashooyinka",
        "Emissions testing requirement": "Shuruudda tijaabinta qiiqa",
        "Employer policy": "Siyaasadda shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada",
        "Employment Authorization": "Oggolaanshaha Shaqada",
        "Employment paperwork": "Waraaqaha shaqada",
        "Endorsement requirements if already licensed": "Shuruudaha aqoonsiga haddii horay shati lagu haysto",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary permits, and continuing education requirements vary by state and profession.": "Aqoonsiga, isweydaarsiga, oggolaanshooyinka ku meel gaarka ah, iyo shuruudaha waxbarashada sii socota way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka iyo xirfadda kasta.",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary practice, and continuing education.": "Aqoonsiga, isweydaarsiga, dhaqanka ku meel gaarka ah, iyo waxbarashada sii socota.",
        "Enhanced or REAL ID": "Enhanced ama REAL ID",
        "Establishing a new permanent residence in the destination state.": "Aasaaska guri joogto ah oo cusub gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "Eviction and late-fee rules": "Qawaaniinta saaridda iyo dib-u-dhaca lacagta",
        "Example checklist categories": "Tusaalooyin qaybaha liiska hubinta",
        "Exploring options. Receive a broad overview checklist.": "Sahaminta doorashooyinka. Hel liis hubin oo dulmar ballaaran.",
        "F-1 OPT and STEM OPT specific. Use verify with the DSO and SEVP Portal guidance. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Do not advise on a specific status outcome.": "F-1 OPT iyo STEM OPT si gaar ah. U isticmaal 'ku hubi DSO-ga iyo hagidda SEVP Portal'. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado (luqadda gunaanad sharci iyo luqadda ka fogaanshaha ciqaabta). Ha bixin talo natiijo xaalad gaar ah.",
        "F-1 specific. Frame as verify with both DSOs and reference Study in the States or ICE materials. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1 si gaar ah. U qaab dheh ku hubi labada DSO oo tixraac qalabka Study in the States ama ICE. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "F-1 students on post-completion OPT or a STEM OPT extension generally use the SEVP Portal or work with their DSO to update physical and mailing address, employer information, and other personal data, typically within 10 days of a change. Unemployment-day limits during OPT continue to apply during and after a move.": "Ardayda F-1 ee ku jira OPT ka dib-dhammaystirka ama kordhinta STEM OPT guud ahaan waxay isticmaalaan SEVP Portal ama waxay la shaqeeyaan DSO-gooda si ay u cusboonaysiiyaan cinwaanka jirka iyo boostada, macluumaadka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, iyo xog kale oo shakhsi ah, sida caadiga ah 10 maalmood gudahood isbeddelka. Xayiraadaha maalmaha shaqo-la'aanta inta lagu jiro OPT waxay sii khusayaan inta iyo ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q specific. Frame as items to verify with IRS guidance and the employer. Do not state that a particular worker is exempt from FICA. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1, J-1, M-1, iyo Q si gaar ah. U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo hagidda IRS iyo shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada. Ha sheegin shaqaale gaar ah uu ka madax-bannan yahay FICA. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Factors that may affect residency for tuition, taxes, licensing, benefits.": "Arrimaha laga yaabo inay saamayn ku yeeshaan degenaanshaha kharashka waxbarashada, canshuuraha, shatiga, manaafacaadyada.",
        "Failing to register on time may affect eligibility for federal benefits, federal jobs, and naturalization later, even though the requirement is federal. State DMV workflows can also trigger automatic registration, which applicants should understand before applying.": "Diidmada diiwaangelinta wakhtigeeda waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa u qalmitaanka manaafacaadyada federaalka, shaqooyinka federaalka, iyo dhalashada goor dambe, in kasta oo shuruuddu ay tahay federaal. Shaqada DMV-da gobolka ayaa sidoo kale kicin karta diiwaangelin toos ah, taas oo codsadayaashu ay tahay inay fahmaan ka hor codsiga.",
        "Family move": "Guuritaanka qoyska",
        "Federal HealthCare.gov guidance describes a list of immigration statuses considered lawfully present for purposes of the Affordable Care Act marketplace, which includes many common nonimmigrant categories. These categories can purchase coverage without a five-year waiting period that applies in many Medicaid contexts.": "Hagidda HealthCare.gov ee federaalka waxay qeexaysaa liis xaaladaha socdaalka ee loo tixgaliyo joogitaan sharci ah ujeeddooyinka suuqa Affordable Care Act, oo ay ku jiraan qaybo aan-socdaal-doon oo caadi ah. Qaybahaani waxay iibsan karaan caymis iyada oon la sugin muddada shanta sano ee khusaysa xaalado Medicaid badan.",
        "Federal Medicaid and CHIP rules generally include a five-year waiting period for many qualified non-citizens after obtaining qualified status, with several federal exceptions. States may use an option that removes the waiting period for children and pregnant people, and some states cover certain groups with state funds.": "Qawaaniinta Medicaid iyo CHIP ee federaalka guud ahaan waxay ku jiraan muddada sugitaanka shanta sano ee qaar badan oo aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn oo u qalma ka dib markay helaan xaalad u qalanta, oo leh dhowr marka laga reebo ee federaalka. Gobolladu waxay isticmaali karaan ikhtiyaar ka saara muddada sugitaanka carruurta iyo dadka uurka leh, qaar ka mid ah gobolladuna waxay ku daboolaan kooxo gaar ah lacag gobol.",
        "Federal Medicare guidance generally describes eligibility for non-citizens who are lawfully admitted for permanent residence and have lived in the United States for five continuous years. Federal Medicaid rules for most nonimmigrants are narrower than for LPRs, with state-specific options for emergency Medicaid and for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "Hagidda Medicare federaalka guud ahaan waxay qeexaysaa u qalmitaanka aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee si sharci ah loogu soo dhoweeyay degenaansho joogto ah oo ku noolaaday Mareykanka shan sano oo isku xiga. Qawaaniinta Medicaid federaalka ee inta badan aan-socdaal-doon ah way ka cidhiidhi yihiin kuwa LPR, oo leh doorashooyin gobol gaar ah ee Medicaid degdeg ah iyo carruurta iyo dadka uurka leh ee sida sharci ah u degan.",
        "Federal REAL ID rules require evidence of lawful status, and many states issue a REAL ID to nonimmigrant visa holders only with an expiration date that does not extend past the I-94, the visa, or another underlying federal document. Implementation differs between states, and standard (non-REAL-ID) options may or may not be offered.": "Qawaaniinta REAL ID ee federaalku waxay u baahan yihiin caddaynta xaaladda sharciga, gobollo badan ayaa siiya REAL ID haystayaasha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah keliya taariikh dhicitaan ah oo aan ka bixin I-94, fiisaha, ama dukumenti federaal kale oo hoosta yaal. Hirgelintu way ka kala duwan tahay gobollada, doorashooyinka caadiga ah (aan-REAL-ID ahayn)na laga yaabaa in la bixiyo iyo in kale.",
        "Federal SNAP, TANF, and similar programs apply a waiting period to many qualified non-citizens. Some states use state funds to operate replacement or supplemental programs that cover groups not eligible for the federal program, with differing rules.": "SNAP, TANF, iyo barnaamijyada la mid ah federaalku waxay khusayaan muddada sugitaanka qaar badan oo aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn oo u qalma. Gobollo qaar waxay lacagta gobolka u isticmaalaan inay maamulaan barnaamijyo beddel ama dheeri ah oo dabool kooxaha aan u qalmin barnaamijka federaalka, oo leh qawaaniin kala duwan.",
        "Federal law": "Sharciga federaalka",
        "Federal law (INA section 265) generally directs non-citizens to report a change of address to USCIS within 10 days of moving, typically through Form AR-11 or the USCIS online change-of-address tool. The federal filing is separate from updating a state DMV record, an employer, a school, or the U.S. Postal Service.": "Sharciga federaalka (INA qaybta 265) wuxuu guud ahaan u tilmaamayaa aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn inay USCIS u soo sheegaan isbeddelka cinwaanka 10 maalmood gudahood guuritaanka, sida caadiga ah iyada oo loo marayo Foomka AR-11 ama qalabka cinwaan-bedelka onlaynka ee USCIS. Gudbinta federaalku waa ka gooni cusboonaysiinta diiwaanka DMV-da gobolka, shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, dugsiga, ama Adeegga Boostada Mareykanka.",
        "Federal law generally requires motor vehicle offices to offer voter registration to applicants, and forms are screened for citizenship attestations. Non-citizens generally are not eligible to register for federal elections, and a registration record can later create immigration complications.": "Sharciga federaalku guud ahaan wuxuu u baahan yahay xafiisyada gawaarida inay codsadayaasha bixiyaan diiwaangelinta codbixinta, foomamkana waxa loo eegaa caddaynta muwaadinimada. Aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn guud ahaan uma qalmaan inay isdiiwaangeliyaan doorashooyinka federaalka, diiwaan diiwaangelin ah ayaa goor dambe abuuri kara dhibaatooyin socdaal.",
        "Federal residency for tax purposes determines whether worldwide income is reported, which IRS forms apply, and how an interstate move's first and last year are filed at the federal level, separately from state residency rules.": "Degenaanshaha federaalka ee ujeeddooyinka canshuurta wuxuu go'aamiyaa inay la soo sheego dakhliga adduunka, foomamka IRS ee khusayaa, iyo sida sannadka koowaad iyo dambe ee u guuritaanka gobol-dhaafka ah loogu gudbiyo heerka federaalka, oo ka gooni ah qawaaniinta degenaanshaha gobolka.",
        "Federal rules govern which immigration statuses can purchase coverage and receive financial help through the Affordable Care Act marketplace, and those rules have changed. State-based marketplaces and state-funded programs add another layer that can differ between origin and destination.": "Qawaaniinta federaalku waxay maamulayaan xaaladaha socdaalka ee iibsan karaan caymiska oo helsi kaalmada maaliyadeed iyada oo loo marayo suuqa Affordable Care Act, qawaaniintaasna way isbeddeleen. Suuqyada gobolka iyo barnaamijyada lacag gobol-leh waxay ku daraan lakab kale oo u kala duwanaan kara u dhaxeeyo gobollada aad ka soo kacaysid iyo aad u socotid.",
        "Federal tax authority": "Maamulka canshuurta federaalka",
        "Federal tax authority general guidance": "Hagid guud oo maamulka canshuurta federaalka",
        "Filing Requirements, Residency, and Telecommuting FAQs": "Shuruudaha Gudbinta, Degenaanshaha, iyo Su'aalaha Inta Badan La Iwedyiiyo ee Telecommuting",
        "Flags risk levels so you know where to focus": "Wuxuu calaamadiyaa heerarka khatarta si aad u ogaato meesha aad diiradda saari karto",
        "Florida Board of Governors page on residency for tuition purposes for the State University System. flbog.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Bogga Florida Board of Governors ee degenaanshaha ujeeddooyinka kharashka waxbarashada ee State University System. flbog.edu wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (Cloudflare); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan.",
        "Florida FLHSMV documentation page for nonimmigrant applicants for driver licenses and identification cards.": "Bogga dukumentiyada Florida FLHSMV ee codsadayaasha aan-socdaal-doon ah ee shatiyada darawalnimada iyo kaadhadhka aqoonsiga.",
        "Follow device language": "Raac luuqadda qalabka",
        "For L-1, whether the new worksite is the same qualifying U.S. office described in the petition or a different one": "Xaaladda L-1, inay goobta shaqada ee cusub ay tahay xafiis Mareykan oo u qalma oo isku mid ah kii lagu sheegay codsiga ama mid kale",
        "For L-1A, L-1B, and O-1 status, USCIS treats a move to a new worksite as a material change in some fact patterns and not others, depending on what the original petition described and whether the new location is consistent with the approved terms. The analysis follows the underlying petition, not LCA-based MSA rules.": "Xaaladda L-1A, L-1B, iyo O-1, USCIS waxay u qaadaa u guuritaanka goob shaqo oo cusub sida isbeddel muhiim ah qaab xaalado qaar ka mid ah, ee ma ahan kuwa kale, iyada oo ku xiran waxa codsiga asalka ah uu sheegay iyo inay goobta cusub ay la mid tahay shuruudaha la oggolaaday. Falanqaynta waxay raacaa codsiga hoosta yaal, ee ma ahan qawaaniinta MSA ee LCA-saleysan.",
        "For O-1, whether the new venue, event, engagement, or agent arrangement falls within the approved petition scope": "Xaaladda O-1, inay goob, dhacdo, ka qaybgal, ama heshiis wakiil oo cusub ku dhaco baaxadda codsiga la oggolaaday",
        "For federal tax purposes, a non-citizen is generally treated as a resident alien if they meet the Substantial Presence Test or hold lawful permanent resident status, with separate rules in IRS Publication 519 for exempt individuals (such as certain F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q students and scholars) whose days of presence may not count.": "Ujeeddooyinka canshuurta federaalka, aan-muwaadin guud ahaan waxa loola dhaqmaa sida resident alien haddii ay buuxiyaan Substantial Presence Test ama ay haystaan xaaladda degane joogto ah oo sharci ah, oo leh qawaaniin gooni ah Daabacaadda IRS 519 ee shakhsiyaadka laga reebay (sida ardayda F-1, J-1, M-1, iyo Q-da qaarkood) oo aanay maalmaha joogitaankooda lagu tirinin.",
        "For nursing specifically, how the destination state treats primary state of residency under the Nurse Licensure Compact for a non-citizen who declares either the country of origin or the compact state, and any credentials-evaluation requirement (for example, CGFNS) for internationally educated applicants": "Si gaar ah kalkaalisada, sida gobolka aad u socotid uu ula dhaqmo gobolka aasaasiga ah ee degenaanshaha hoos imanaysa Nurse Licensure Compact aan-muwaadin ku dhawaaqaya labadaba dalka aasaaska ama gobolka heshiiska, iyo shuruud qiimaynta-aqoonsiga (tusaale, CGFNS) codsadayaasha caalami ah waxbarashada laga qaaday",
        "Form AR-11 paper version posted on uscis.gov.": "Nooca warqada ee Foomka AR-11 oo lagu dhejiyay uscis.gov.",
        "Frame AR-11 as a federal reporting step to verify, not a guarantee of status. Do not state that any specific status category is or is not covered without source. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing such as the i-word, the p-words, and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney for status-specific guidance.": "U qaab dheh AR-11 sida tallaabo warbixin federaal oo la hubinayo, ee ma aha damaanad xaaladda. Ha sheegin in qayb xaaladeed gaar ah la daboolay ama aan la daboolin iyada oon isha la haynin. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado (luqadda gunaanad sharci sida 'i-word', 'p-words', iyo luqadda ka fogaanshaha ciqaabta). U tilmaan akhristayaasha inay la tashadaan qareen socdaal oo shati haysta hagid xaalad gaar ah.",
        "Frame as a federal requirement that may apply, with a nonimmigrant exception that may apply based on continuous valid status. Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida shuruud federaal oo laga yaabo inay khusayso, oo leh marka aan-socdaal-doon ah oo laga reebay oo laga yaabo inay khusayso oo ku saleysan xaalad ansax ah oo sii socota. Ha sheegin in qof gaar ah loo baahan yahay ama loo baahnayn in la diiwaangaliyo. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Frame as items to verify in IRS Publication 519 and with a qualified tax preparer. Do not state a person is a dual-status filer for a particular year. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo Daabacaadda IRS 519 iyo diyaariye canshuur oo aqoonsan. Ha sheegin qof yahay file xaalad labanlaha ah sannad gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Frame as items to verify with CMS and the destination-state Medicaid agency. Federal rules have changed and may continue to change. Do not state a person is or is not eligible. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo CMS iyo hay'adda Medicaid ee gobolka aad u socotid. Qawaaniinta federaalku way isbeddeleen waxayna sii isbeddeli karaan. Ha sheegin qof yahay ama aanu ahayn mid u qalma. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Frame as items to verify with IRS Publication 519 and a tax preparer. Do not state a person is or is not a resident alien for federal tax purposes. Use may apply and rules differ by jurisdiction. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo Daabacaadda IRS 519 iyo diyaariye canshuur. Ha sheegin qof yahay ama aanu ahayn resident alien ujeeddooyinka canshuurta federaalka. U isticmaal 'waxaa laga yaabaa inay khusayso' iyo 'sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta'. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Frame as items to verify with the DSO or J-1 sponsor and Study in the States or ICE guidance. This item is specific to F-1, M-1, and J-1 status. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo DSO ama kafiilka J-1 iyo hagidda Study in the States ama ICE. Cinwaankan waxa loogu talagalay xaaladda F-1, M-1, iyo J-1. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado (luqadda gunaanad sharci iyo luqadda ka fogaanshaha ciqaabta).",
        "Frame as items to verify with the current HealthCare.gov or state-based marketplace lists. Do not state any specific category is or is not on the lawfully present list, since federal rules have changed. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "U qaab dheh sida cinwaano lagu hubinayo liisaska hadda ee HealthCare.gov ama suuqa gobol-saleysan. Ha sheegin in qayb gaar ah ay ku jirto ama aanay ku jirin liiska joogitaanka sharciga, maaddaama qawaaniinta federaalku isbedeleen. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Full disclaimer:": "Af-celinta dhammaystiran:",
        "General information only. Not legal advice. Verify with official sources.": "Macluumaad guud oo keliya. Ma aha talo sharci. Ku hubi ilaha rasmiga ah.",
        "General information only. Verify with the relevant official source. Not legal advice.": "Macluumaad guud oo keliya. Ku hubi isha rasmiga ah ee la xiriira. Ma aha talo sharci.",
        "Generate checklist": "Abuur liis hubinta",
        "Generated:": "La sameeyay:",
        "Generates a checklist of topics to verify before moving": "Wuxuu abuuraa liis hubin oo mowduucyo aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso ka hor guuritaanka",
        "Georgia Department of Driver Services page for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including a 30-day rule for establishing Georgia residency.": "Bogga Georgia Department of Driver Services ee codsadayaasha aan-muwaadiniinta U.S.-ahayn, oo ay ku jirto qaanuun 30-maalmood ah oo aasaaska degenaanshaha Georgia.",
        "Get a grouped checklist with risk badges and links to official sources.": "Hel liis hubin oo kooxaysan oo leh calaamado khatar iyo xiriiriyeyaal isaha rasmiga ah.",
        "H-1B specific. Frame as verify with employer counsel and USCIS or DOL guidance. Do not state that an amendment is or is not required in a particular fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "H-1B si gaar ah. U qaab dheh ku hubi qareenka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada iyo hagidda USCIS ama DOL. Ha sheegin in beddelku la baahan yahay ama aan loo baahnayn qaab xaalado gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "H-1B specific. Use verify whether MSA boundaries cover the new worksite. Do not assert that no amendment is needed in any specific fact pattern. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "H-1B si gaar ah. U isticmaal 'hubi inay xudduudaha MSA daboolaan goobta shaqada cusub'. Ha sheegin in beddel loo baahnayn xaalad gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "HOW IT WORKS": "SIDUU U SHAQEEYO",
