        "Highlights stale or placeholder sources": "Wuxuu iftiimiyaa ilaha duugay ama kuwa boos-haye ah",
        "Housing / renter basics": "Aasaaska guryaha / kireystaha",
        "How CHIP coverage rules in the destination state interact with the waiting period for your household": "Sida qawaaniinta caymiska CHIP ee gobolka aad u socotid ay ula falgashan karto muddada sugitaanka qoyskaaga",
        "How OPT or STEM OPT employment is treated for FICA while the worker remains a nonresident alien": "Sida loola dhaqmo shaqada OPT ama STEM OPT ee FICA halka shaqaaluhu weli yahay nonresident alien",
        "How a future change to LPR status before age 26 may affect the registration question": "Sida isbeddelka mustaqbalka ee xaaladda LPR ka hor da'da 26 uu u saamayn karo su'aasha diiwaangelinta",
        "How a mid-year move between states may affect aid-application deadlines": "Sida u guuritaanka bartamaha sano ee u dhaxeeyo gobollada uu u saamayn karo kama dambaysta codsiga kaalmada",
        "How a move mid-coverage may affect the reasonable opportunity period for documentation": "Sida u guuritaanka bartamaha caymiska uu u saamayn karo muddada fursadda macquulka ah ee dukumentiyada",
        "How a transfer interacts with current employment authorization, on-campus work, and any pending OPT": "Sida u wareejintu ula falgasho oggolaanshaha shaqada hadda, shaqada kambaska, iyo OPT kasta oo sugaya",
        "How a year of arrival to or departure from the United States interacts with the test": "Sida sannadka imaanshaha ama bixitaanka Mareykanka uu ula falgasho tijaabada",
        "How an in-progress extension of status (for example, an H-1B amendment or an F-1 transfer) interacts with renewing or replacing the credential": "Sida kordhinta xaaladda ee horumarsan (tusaale, beddel H-1B ama u wareejin F-1) ay ula falgasho cusboonaysiinta ama beddelka aqoonsiga",
        "How clinical-placement and background-check requirements interact with your immigration status": "Sida shuruudaha meelaynta isbitaalka iyo baaritaanka asalku ay ula falgasho xaaladdaada socdaalka",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification": "Muddada aad u baahan tahay inaad degenaansho ka haysato gobolka aad u socotid ka hor inta aan lagu tixgalin kala saaridda gobol-gudaha",
        "How long you must hold residency in the destination state before being considered for in-state classification, and whether time on a nonimmigrant visa counts": "Muddada aad u baahan tahay inaad degenaansho ka haysato gobolka aad u socotid ka hor inta aan lagu tixgalin kala saaridda gobol-gudaha, iyo inay wakhtiga aad ku jirtay fiise aan-socdaal-doon ah la tirinayo",
        "How temporary stay is treated differently from permanent relocation": "Sida joogitaanka ku meel gaarka ah si kala duwan loogu qaado guuritaanka joogtada ah",
        "How the destination state defines residency": "Sida gobolka aad u socotid uu u qeexo degenaanshaha",
        "How the destination state's DMV or other application workflows interact with Selective Service screening": "Sida DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid ama shaqada codsiga kale ay ula falgasho baaritaanka Selective Service",
        "How the move affects any STEM OPT Form I-983 training plan and the destination employer's E-Verify status": "Sida guuritaanku uu u saamayn karo qorshe tababar Foomka I-983 ee STEM OPT iyo xaaladda E-Verify ee shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada ee aad u socotid",
        "How the move and any change in employer-sponsored coverage interact with marketplace special enrollment timing": "Sida guuritaanku iyo isbeddel kasta oo caymis-kafiilkaagu uu bixiyo ay ula falgashan karaan wakhtiga isdiiwaangelinta gaarka ah ee suuqa",
        "How the move interacts with H-4 dependent status and any pending I-485 or I-140": "Sida guuritaanku ula falgasho xaaladda ku-tiirsanaan H-4 iyo I-485 ama I-140 kasta oo sugaya",
        "How to confirm a registration after applying for a license": "Sida loo xaqiijiyo diiwaangelin ka dib codsiga shatiga",
        "How to correct the record if a non-citizen registration was submitted in error": "Sida loo saxo diiwaanka haddii diiwaangelin aan-muwaadin ah si khalad ah loo gudbiyo",
        "How to decline voter registration when offered at the DMV in that state": "Sida loo diido diiwaangelinta codbixinta marka lagu bixiyo DMV-da gobolkaas",
        "How to obtain or replace a Selective Service registration record if needed for future immigration or federal-benefit filings": "Sida loo helo ama loo beddelo diiwaanka diiwaangelinta Selective Service haddii loo baahdo gudbinta socdaalka ama manaafacaadka federaalka ee mustaqbalka",
        "How unemployment days are counted during a gap between employers around a move": "Sida maalmaha shaqo-la'aanta lagu tiriyo inta lagu jiro farqi u dhexeeyo shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada agagaarka guuritaanka",
