        "I'm on a nonimmigrant visa (F-1, H-1B, J-1, etc.)": "Waxaan ku jiraa fiise aan-socdaal-doon ah (F-1, H-1B, J-1, iwm.)",
        "ICE SEVIS landing page.": "Bogga aasaasiga ah ee ICE SEVIS.",
        "ICE SEVIS overview page for background context on F, M, and J record management.": "Bogga dulmar ICE SEVIS oo bixiya macluumaad asal ah oo ku saabsan maaraynta diiwaanka F, M, iyo J.",
