        "ICE Transfers for F-1 Students": "ICE U Wareejinta Ardayda F-1",
        "ICE page describing F-1 SEVIS transfers.": "Bogga ICE oo qeexaya u wareejinta F-1 SEVIS.",
        "IRS Aliens Employed in the U.S. Social Security Taxes": "IRS Aliens-ka Shaqaalaha U.S. Canshuurta Social Security",
        "IRS Determining an Individuals Tax Residency Status": "IRS Go'aaminta Xaaladda Degenaanshaha Canshuurta Shakhsiga",
        "IRS Foreign Student Liability for Social Security and Medicare Taxes": "IRS Mas'uuliyadda Ardayga Shisheeye ee Canshuurta Social Security iyo Medicare",
        "IRS Publication 519 U.S. Tax Guide for Aliens": "IRS Daabacaadda 519 U.S. Hagidda Canshuurta ee Aliens",
        "IRS Publication 519 describes a dual-status tax year for non-citizens who are both a nonresident and a resident for federal tax purposes during the same year, which can apply to many arrival, departure, and adjustment-of-status fact patterns rather than interstate moves alone.": "Daabacaadda IRS 519 waxay qeexaysaa sannad canshuureed xaalad labanlaha ah ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee labadaba nonresident iyo resident ujeeddooyinka canshuurta federaalka inta lagu jiro sannadka isku mid ah, taas oo khusayn karta xaalado badan oo imaanshaha, bixitaanka, iyo hagaajinta-xaaladda halkii ay khusayn lahayd guuritaanka gobol-dhaafka ah keligeed.",
        "IRS Publication 519 main page.": "Bogga ugu weyn ee Daabacaadda IRS 519.",
        "IRS Taxation of Dual-Status Individuals": "IRS Canshuurta Shakhsiyaadka Xaaladda Labanlaha ah",
        "IRS Taxation of Nonresident Aliens": "IRS Canshuurta Nonresident Aliens",
        "IRS dual-status filer page. Final redirected URL uses the dual-status-individuals slug.": "Bogga filerada xaaladda labanlaha ah ee IRS. URL-ka kama dambaysta loo wareejiyo wuxuu isticmaalaa slug dual-status-individuals.",
        "IRS general page on taxation of nonresident aliens.": "Bogga guud ee IRS ee canshuurta nonresident aliens.",
        "IRS guidance generally describes an exemption from FICA tax for wages paid for services performed by F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q nonresident-alien students, scholars, teachers, researchers, and trainees, when the work is part of the activity for which they were admitted and they remain nonresident aliens for federal tax purposes.": "Hagidda IRS guud ahaan waxay qeexaysaa marka laga reebay canshuurta FICA mushaharka loo bixiyo adeegyada ay qabtaan ardayda, cilmi-baarayaasha, macallimiinta, iyo tababaranayaasha F-1, J-1, M-1, iyo Q ee nonresident-alien, marka shaqadu ay qayb ka tahay howsha loo soo dhoweeyay ay weli yihiin nonresident aliens ujeeddooyinka canshuurta federaalka.",
        "IRS overview page for non-citizen tax residency status.": "Bogga dulmar IRS oo ku saabsan xaaladda degenaanshaha canshuurta ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn.",
        "IRS page describing the Substantial Presence Test for federal tax residency.": "Bogga IRS oo qeexaya Substantial Presence Test ee degenaanshaha canshuurta federaalka.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for F, J, M, Q nonresident-alien students and scholars.": "Bogga IRS ee qaabilaadda canshuurta FICA ee ardayda iyo cilmi-baarayaasha F, J, M, Q nonresident-alien.",
        "IRS page on FICA tax treatment for non-citizens employed in the U.S.": "Bogga IRS ee qaabilaadda canshuurta FICA ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee shaqaaleeysiiyay U.S.",
        "IV. Residency - The City University of New York Tuition and Fee Manual": "IV. Degenaanshaha - The City University of New York Tuition and Fee Manual",
        "Identification Requirements": "Shuruudaha Aqoonsiga",
        "Identity and residency documents accepted by the destination state": "Dukumentiyada aqoonsi iyo degenaansho ee uu aqbalo gobolka aad u socotid",
        "If a credential is issued with an unexpected short term tied to a federal document, the timing of renewal can affect domestic flights, federal building access, and other tasks that may rely on a REAL ID after a move.": "Haddii aqoonsi la bixiyo oo leh muddo gaaban oo aan la fileyn oo ku xidhan dukumenti federaal, wakhtiga cusboonaysiintu waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa duulimaadyada gudaha, gelitaanka dhismaha federaalka, iyo waxqabadyada kale ee laga yaabo inay ku tiirsanaadaan REAL ID ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "Illinois Board of Higher Education directory page on campus liaisons supporting students under state tuition-equity provisions.": "Bogga buug-tilmaameedka Illinois Board of Higher Education ee xidhiidhiyeyaasha kambaska oo taageeraya ardayda hoos imanaysa qodobada sinaanta kharashka waxbarashada ee gobolka.",
        "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL) page. ilsos.gov returns a 302 redirect to its own page for curl HEAD requests, which is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov domain; the URL was confirmed via the Secretary of State's own search index.": "Bogga Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL). ilsos.gov wuxuu soo celiyaa wareejin 302 ee bogiisa codsiyada curl HEAD, taas oo la yaqaan oo been ah oo taban oo domain .gov ah; URL-ka waxa lagu xaqiijiyay diiwaanka raadinta ee Secretary of State-ka.",
        "Illinois Student Assistance Commission resources page for non-U.S. citizen students including RISE Act and Alternative Application context. isac.org returns 403 to non-browser requests (anti-bot); this is a known false negative.": "Bogga khayraadka Illinois Student Assistance Commission ee ardayda aan-muwaadiniinta U.S.-ahayn oo ay ku jiraan RISE Act iyo Alternative Application. isac.org wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (ka-hortagga botka); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan.",
        "Immigration status - including Dreamer / DACA status - can significantly affect driver's licenses and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing and healthcare), in-state tuition, SSN-related requirements, and state tax filing. Rules vary by state and federal law and change frequently.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney before relying on any state-by-state summary.": "Xaaladda socdaalka - oo ay ku jirto xaaladda Dreamer / DACA - waxay si weyn u saamayn kartaa shatiyada darawalnimada iyo REAL ID, shatiga xirfadda (gaar ahaan kalkaalisada iyo daryeelka caafimaadka), kharashka waxbarashada ee gobolka, shuruudaha la xiriira SSN, iyo gudbinta canshuurta gobolka. Sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta iyo sharciga federaalka, waxayna isbeddelaan si joogto ah.\n\nMoveSafe ma aha bedel u ah talada sharci. Ka fiirso inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta aadan ku tiirsanaan koobid gobol-ka-gobol.",
        "Immunization requirements": "Shuruudaha tallaalka",
        "Important to verify": "Muhiim in la hubiyo",
        "Information for Non-US Citizens": "Macluumaadka Aan-Muwaadiniinta US-Ahayn",
        "Inspection requirement": "Shuruudda kormeerka",
        "Insurance networks, Medicaid and marketplace rules, and prescription transfer processes vary by state.": "Shabakadaha caymiska, qawaaniinta Medicaid iyo suuqa, iyo hababka u wareejinta dawooyinku way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta.",
        "Insurance networks, student health, prescriptions, primary care access.": "Shabakadaha caymiska, caafimaadka ardayga, dawooyinka, helitaanka daryeelka aasaasiga ah.",
        "Internship": "Tababarka shaqo",
        "J-1 specific. Frame as verify with the program sponsor and reference 22 CFR Part 62. Do not state that any specific category does or does not require sponsor pre-approval for a particular change. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "J-1 si gaar ah. U qaab dheh ku hubi kafiilka barnaamijka oo tixraac 22 CFR Qaybta 62. Ha sheegin in qayb gaar ah ay u baahan tahay ama aanay u baahnayn oggolaansho hore oo kafiil isbeddel gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Jurisdiction: %@": "Xukunka: %@",
        "Know how to respond if asked to register to vote at the DMV": "Ogow sida looga jawaabo haddii laguu sheego inaad isdiiwaangeliso codbixin DMV-da",
        "L-1 and O-1 specific. Frame as verify against the approved petition and consult petitioner counsel. Do not state that an amendment is or is not needed for any specific scenario. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "L-1 iyo O-1 si gaar ah. U qaab dheh ku hubi codsiga la oggolaaday oo la tasho qareenka codsadaha. Ha sheegin in beddel loo baahan yahay ama loo baahnayn xaalad gaar ah. Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado.",
        "Language": "Luuqadda",
        "Last verified:": "Hubinta u dambeysay:",
        "Last verified: %@": "Hubinta u dambeysay: %@",
        "Lawful permanent residents (LPRs / green card holders) can face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing - foreign credentials evaluation may apply), Medicaid and state-marketplace eligibility (the federal 5-year bar interacts with state programs), state tax filing, and how DMVs handle voter-registration prompts (LPRs are not eligible to vote in federal or most state elections).\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney for status-affecting questions and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Degane joogto ah oo sharci ah (LPR / haystayaasha kaadhka cagaaran) waxay la kulmi karaan kala duwanaansho gobol-ka-gobol oo ku saabsan dukumentiyada shatiga darawalnimada iyo REAL ID, shatiga xirfadda (gaar ahaan kalkaalisada - qiimaynta aqoonsiga shisheeye laga yaabo inay khusayso), u qalmitaanka Medicaid iyo suuqa gobolka (xayiraadda 5-sano ee federaalka ayaa la falgashada barnaamijyada gobolka), gudbinta canshuurta gobolka, iyo sida DMV-yadu u qabtaan codsiyada diiwaangelinta codbixiyaha (LPR-yada uma qalmayaan inay ka codeeyaan doorashooyinka federaalka iyo inta badan kuwa gobolka).\n\nMoveSafe ma aha bedel u ah talada sharci. Ka fiirso inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ee su'aalaha saamaynta ku leh xaaladda, iyo xirfadle canshuur oo aqoonsan ee gudbinta gobol-dhaafka ah.",
        "Lease decisions made based on origin-state assumptions may not match destination-state rules.": "Go'aamada heshiiska kirada ee lagu saleeyo malaha gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid laga yaabaa inaanay la mid noqon qawaaniinta gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "Lease terms, security deposits, notice periods, and tenant protections.": "Shuruudaha kirada, deebaajiga ammaanka, muddooyinka ogeysiiska, iyo ilaalinta kireystaha.",
        "Legal aid (general info)": "Kaalmo sharci (macluumaad guud)",
        "License transfer, deadlines, documents, and REAL ID awareness.": "U wareejinta shatiga, kama dambaysta, dukumentiyada, iyo wacyigelinta REAL ID.",
        "Licensure Compacts - NCSBN": "Heshiisyada Shatiga - NCSBN",
        "Licensure requirements can affect clinical placement, NCLEX eligibility, endorsement, and employment timing.": "Shuruudaha shatigu waxay saamayn ku yeelan karaan meelaynta isbitaalka, u qalmitaanka NCLEX, aqoonsiga, iyo wakhtiga shaqada.",
        "Links to official state agency sources": "Wuxuu ku xirayaa ilaha hay'adaha rasmiga ah ee gobolka",
        "Load example": "Soo geli tusaalaha",
        "Local city/county rules may add protections. Review lease language directly.": "Qawaaniinta magaalada/gobolka deegaanka ayaa laga yaabaa inay ku darto ilaalin. Si toos ah u eeg luqadda heshiiska kirada.",
        "Local ordinance": "Qaanuunka deegaanka",
        "Local pet licensing requirements": "Shuruudaha shatiga xayawaanka guriga ee deegaanka",
        "Main USCIS page for H-1B specialty occupations classification.": "Bogga ugu weyn ee USCIS ee kala saaridda shaqooyinka takhasuska H-1B.",
        "Many nonimmigrant visa holders are not within the standard Medicare or Medicaid eligibility groups, and federal rules in this area have been changing. Destination-state Medicaid rules add another layer that may differ from origin-state rules.": "Haystayaal badan oo fiise aan-socdaal-doon ah ah ma ku jiraan kooxaha u qalmitaanka caadiga ah ee Medicare ama Medicaid, qawaaniinta federaalka ee aaggana way isbeddeleen. Qawaaniinta Medicaid ee gobolka aad u socotid waxay ku daraan lakab kale oo u kala duwanaan kara qawaaniinta gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid.",
        "Many states require new residents to obtain a state driver's license within a specific period after becoming a resident.": "Gobollo badan waxay u baahan yihiin in degane cusub helo shatiga darawalnimada ee gobolka muddo gaar ah ka dib markay noqdaan degane.",
        "Mark as not verified": "Calaamadi inaan la xaqiijinin",
        "Mark as verified": "Calaamadi inay la xaqiijiyay",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for nonresidents using Form 1-NR/PY. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Hagidda Massachusetts Department of Revenue ee canshuurta dakhliga shakhsiga ee nonresidents iyada oo la isticmaalayo Foomka 1-NR/PY. mass.gov wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (Cloudflare); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan.",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for part-year residents. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Hagidda Massachusetts Department of Revenue ee canshuurta dakhliga shakhsiga ee deganayaasha qayb-sano ah. mass.gov wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (Cloudflare); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan.",
        "Massachusetts RMV identification requirements page covering REAL ID, standard licenses, and lawful presence documentation. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov-hosted state portal.": "Bogga shuruudaha aqoonsiga Massachusetts RMV oo daboolaya REAL ID, shatiyada caadiga ah, iyo dukumentiyada joogitaanka sharciga. mass.gov wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (Cloudflare); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan oo bog gobol ah oo .gov-hoy-yaha ah.",
        "Massachusetts identification (ID) requirements": "Shuruudaha aqoonsiga (ID) Massachusetts",
        "May involve penalties or licensing consequences.": "Waxaa laga yaabaa inay ku lug yeesho ciqaabyo ama cawaaqib shati.",
        "Medicare.gov Get Started with Medicare": "Medicare.gov La Bilow Medicare",
        "Minimum coverage, state-specific rules, and policy address updates.": "Daboolida ugu yar, qawaaniinta gobolka u gaarka ah, iyo cusboonaysiinta cinwaanka caymiska.",
        "Missing a school or hospital onboarding requirement can delay clinical hours and graduation timing.": "Seegista shuruudda gelinta dugsiga ama isbitaalka waxay dib u dhigi kartaa saacadaha isbitaalka iyo wakhtiga qalin-jabinta.",
        "Missing a state motor vehicle deadline can create administrative or driving-related problems after relocation.": "Seegista kama dambaysta hay'adda gawaarida ee gobolka waxay abuuri kartaa dhibaatooyin maamul ama wadid la xiriira ka dib guuritaanka.",
        "Missing source": "Isha maqan",
        "Missing the transfer reporting steps at the new school, or letting the transfer release date and program start fall out of sync, can affect status maintenance and access to on-campus work.": "Seegista tallaabooyinka warbixinta u wareejinta dugsiga cusub, ama u oggolaanshaha taariikhda sii-deynta u wareejinta iyo bilaabista barnaamijka inay ka jajaban yihiin, waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa sii-haynta xaaladda iyo helitaanka shaqada kambaska.",
        "Mixed jurisdiction": "Xukun isku dhafan",
        "MoveSafe checklist": "Liiska hubinta MoveSafe",
        "MoveSafe is a source-first checklist tool. It links you to official resources and highlights topics to verify. It does not provide legal advice.": "MoveSafe waa qalab liis hubin oo isha rasmiga ah marka hore u dhigta. Wuxuu kugu xirayaa ilaha rasmiga ah wuxuuna iftiimiyaa mowduucyada aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso. Ma siiyo talooyin sharci.",
        "MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves. You can still build a checklist, but some items may not apply.": "MoveSafe waxaa loogu talagalay guuritaanka gobol-ka-gobol. Weli waad samayn kartaa liis hubin, laakiin qaar ka mid ah cinwaanada laga yaabo inaanay khusayn.",
        "MoveSafe prefers official agency sources. Placeholder entries should be replaced with verified URLs before production use.": "MoveSafe waxa uu door biday ilaha hay'adaha rasmiga ah. Galitaannada boos-haye waa in lagu beddelaa URL-yo la hubiyay ka hor isticmaalka soosaarka.",
        "MoveSafe provides general legal and administrative information based on publicly available sources. It does not provide legal advice, does not create an attorney-client relationship, and should not be used as a substitute for advice from a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction. Laws and agency rules change frequently. Always verify information with official sources before making decisions.": "MoveSafe wuxuu bixiyaa macluumaad guud oo sharci iyo maamul oo ku saleysan ilo dadweynaha la heli karo. Ma bixiyo talooyin sharci, ma abuuro xiriir qareen-macmiil, mana aha in loo isticmaalo bedel u ah talo qareen shati haysta xukunkaaga. Sharciyada iyo qawaaniinta hay'aduhu way isbeddelaan si joogto ah. Mar walba ku hubi macluumaadka ilaha rasmiga ah ka hor inta aadan go'aan gaarin.",
        "Moving across state lines? Know what to verify before you go.": "Ma u guuraysaa gobol kale? Ogow waxa aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso ka hor inta aadan tegin.",
        "Moving for school": "U guuritaan dugsi awgeed",
        "Moving for work": "U guuritaan shaqo awgeed",
        "Moving from %1$@ to %2$@": "Ka guuritaanka %1$@ una guuritaanka %2$@",
        "Moving from one state's aid program to another's may change which aid applications to consider and which documents to gather, and this can affect how to plan tuition and living costs at the destination.": "Ka guuritaanka barnaamijka kaalmada gobol qiyaastiis ee kale waxa uu bedeli karaa codsiyada kaalmada la tixgelinayo iyo dukumentiyada la soo aruurinayo, taasna waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa sida loo qorsheeyo kharashka waxbarashada iyo nolosha ee halka loo socdo.",
        "Moving may change which state tax withholding forms apply, and remote work can create cross-state payroll questions.": "Guuritaanku wuxuu bedeli karaa foomamka hayidda canshuurta gobolka ee khusayaa, shaqada fogna waxay abuuri kartaa su'aalo mushaharka gobol-dhaaf ah.",
        "Moving to another state for clinical rotations, externships, or supervised practice.": "U guuritaan gobol kale wareegyada isbitaalka, ku tababarka, ama dhaqanka la kormeerayo.",
        "NCLEX and license-by-endorsement steps can stall when documentation does not match a destination board's current rules, which can delay clinical placement, hire dates, and compact-state recognition.": "Tallaabooyinka NCLEX iyo shatiga-aqoonsiga ayaa joogsan kara marka dukumentiyadu aanay la mid noqon qawaaniinta hadda ee guddiga aad u socotid, taas oo dib u dhigi karta meelaynta isbitaalka, taariikhaha shaqo qaadashada, iyo aqoonsiga gobolka heshiiska.",
        "NCLEX eligibility requirements": "Shuruudaha u qalmitaanka NCLEX",
        "NCSBN Licensure Compacts overview, including Nurse Licensure Compact context for non-citizen primary state of residency declarations.": "Dulmar Heshiisyada Shatiga NCSBN, oo ay ku jirto macluumaadka Nurse Licensure Compact ee ku dhawaaqida gobolka aasaasiga ah ee degenaanshaha ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn.",
        "National Council of State Boards of Nursing licensure guidance page for background context across boards.": "Bogga hagidda shatiga National Council of State Boards of Nursing ee macluumaadka asalka guddiyada dhammaantood.",
        "New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education page summarizing the Tuition Equality Act and the 2020 statute affecting dependent students of H-1B holders.": "Bogga New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education oo kooba Tuition Equality Act iyo xeerka 2020 ee saamayn ku leh ardayda ku-tiirsanaha ee haystayaasha H-1B.",
        "New York DMV REAL ID page noting that an Enhanced ID is for U.S. citizens only and that REAL ID issued to applicants with temporary lawful status may expire with the federal document.": "Bogga REAL ID ee New York DMV oo tilmaamaya in Enhanced ID uu yahay kaliya ee muwaadiniinta U.S. iyo in REAL ID-ga loo bixiyo codsadayaasha xaalad sharci ku meel gaar ah haysta uu dhici karo dukumentiga federaalka.",
        "New York DMV documentation guidance for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including REAL ID and standard credentials.": "Hagidda dukumentiyada New York DMV ee codsadayaasha aan-muwaadiniinta U.S.-ahayn, oo ay ku jiraan REAL ID iyo aqoonsiyada caadiga ah.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance FAQ on residency, nonresident filing, and telecommuting.": "FAQ New York Department of Taxation and Finance ee degenaanshaha, gudbinta nonresident, iyo telecommuting.",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance page on nonresident and part-year filing using Form IT-203.": "Bogga New York Department of Taxation and Finance ee gudbinta nonresident iyo qayb-sano ah iyada oo la isticmaalayo Foomka IT-203.",
        "New York State Education Department Office of the Professions RN licensure requirements page, which administers nursing licensure for New York.": "Bogga shuruudaha shatiga RN ee New York State Education Department Office of the Professions, oo maamula shatiga kalkaalisada ee New York.",
        "No items match your filters": "Wax cinwaanno ah uma waafaqsana sifeeyayaashaada",
        "No source has been added yet for this item. Add an official source before relying on it.": "Wax isha ah weli looma diirin cinwaankan. Ku dar isha rasmiga ah ka hor inta aadan ku tiirsanaan.",
        "No sources are attached to the items in this view.": "Ma jiraan ilo ku lifaaqan cinwaanada muuqaalkan.",
        "Non-Immigrant - Florida Department of Highway Safety and Motor Vehicles": "Aan-Socdaal-Doon ah - Florida Department of Highway Safety and Motor Vehicles",
        "Nonimmigrant visa holders (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1, and others) face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID (often tied to I-94 / visa dates), in-state tuition (most public universities classify F-1 students as out-of-state), professional licensure documentation, tax residency rules, and health-insurance options. USCIS also requires reporting any address change within 10 days via Form AR-11.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney, your school's DSO if on F-1, employer HR or immigration counsel if on a work visa, and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "Haystayaasha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doonka ahayn (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1, iyo kuwa kale) waxay la kulmaan kala duwanaansho gobol-ka-gobol oo ku saabsan dukumentiyada shatiga darawalnimada iyo REAL ID (badanaa waxay xidhan yihiin taariikhaha I-94 / fiisaha), kharashka waxbarashada ee gobolka (jaamacadaha dadweynaha intooda badan waxay arday F-1 u tixgeliyaan in ay yihiin kuwo aan-gobolka-ahayn), dukumentiyada shatiga xirfadda, sharciyada degenaanshaha canshuurta, iyo doorashooyinka caymiska caafimaadka. USCIS sidoo kale waxa loo baahan yahay in la soo sheego isbeddel kasta oo cinwaan ah 10 maalmood gudahood iyada oo loo marayo Foomka AR-11.\n\nMoveSafe ma aha bedel u ah talada sharci. Ka fiirso inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta, DSO-ga dugsigaaga haddii aad ku jirto F-1, HR-ka shaqaalaha ama qareenka socdaalka haddii aad ku jirto fiisaha shaqada, iyo xirfadle canshuur oo aqoonsan ee gudbinta gobol-dhaafka ah.",
        "Nonresident and part-year resident forms and instructions": "Foomamka iyo tilmaamaha nonresident iyo degane qayb-sano ah",
