        "Pet rules may be set by state, local, or housing-provider policies. Each layer can have different requirements.": "Qawaaniinta xayawaanka guriga waxaa dejin kara siyaasadaha gobolka, deegaanka, ama bixiyaha guryaha. Lakab kastaa wuxuu yeelan karaa shuruudo kala duwan.",
