        "REAL ID and standard credentials use different document checklists and have different uses for federal purposes such as boarding domestic flights or entering certain federal buildings.": "Aqoonsiyada REAL ID iyo caadiga ah waxay isticmaalaan liisas dukumenti oo kala duwan waxayna leeyihiin isticmaalo kala duwan ujeeddooyinka federaalka sida fuulista duulimaadyada gudaha ama gelitaanka dhismeyaal federaal oo qaar ah.",
        "RISK": "KHATAR",
        "RN License Requirements - NYS Office of the Professions": "Shuruudaha Shatiga RN - NYS Office of the Professions",
        "Rabies and other vaccination documentation requirements": "Shuruudaha dukumentiyada tallaalka rabies iyo tallaalada kale",
        "Receiving school registrar / residency office": "Diiwaangeluhu dugsiga la helay / xafiiska degenaanshaha",
        "Recently verified": "Dhowaan la xaqiijiyay",
        "Registering or being recorded as registered, even by mistake, may create issues for naturalization, status renewal, or future immigration filings. The risk of an inadvertent record can depend on how a state's DMV workflow is designed.": "Isdiiwaangelinta ama in lagu duubo isdiiwaangelin, xitaa khalad, waxa laga yaabaa inay abuurto arrimo ku saabsan dhalashada, cusboonaysiinta xaaladda, ama gudbinta socdaalka mustaqbalka. Khatarta diiwaan aan kasoo-shaqo ah waxay ku xirnaan kartaa sida loo qaabeeyey shaqada DMV-da gobolka.",
        "Registration deadline after establishing residency": "Kama dambaysta diiwaangelinta ka dib aasaaska degenaanshaha",
        "Registration deadlines, inspection, emissions, title, and plate rules.": "Kama dambaysta diiwaangelinta, kormeerka, qiiqa, lahaanshaha, iyo qawaaniinta taarikada.",
