        "Relocating for a job or new employer.": "U guuritaan shaqo ama shaqaale bixiye cusub.",
        "Relocating for a nursing or healthcare program (ABSN, MEPN, MSN, allied health, etc.).": "U guuritaan barnaamij kalkaaliye ama daryeel caafimaad (ABSN, MEPN, MSN, daryeelka caafimaad ee la xidhiidha, iwm.).",
        "Relocating to attend an undergraduate or graduate program.": "U guuritaan inaad gasho barnaamij shahaadada koowaad ama sare.",
        "Relocating with family members or dependents.": "U guuritaan iyada oo la wado xubnaha qoyska ama kuwa ku tiirsan.",
        "Replace official agency or licensed-professional guidance": "Beddelidda hagidda hay'adaha rasmiga ah ama xirfadlayaasha shati haysta",
        "Replace with an official URL from the destination state motor vehicle agency before relying on this item.": "Ku beddel URL rasmi ah oo ka socota hay'adda gawaarida ee gobolka aad u socotid ka hor inta aadan ku tiirsanaan cinwaankan.",
        "Replace with an official URL from the origin state motor vehicle agency before relying on this item.": "Ku beddel URL rasmi ah oo ka socota hay'adda gawaarida ee gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid ka hor inta aadan ku tiirsanaan cinwaankan.",
        "Replace with official federal tax-authority guidance. Use only as general orientation; consult a qualified tax professional.": "Ku beddel hagidda rasmiga ah ee maamulka canshuurta federaalka. U isticmaal kaliya sida hag guud; la tasho xirfadle canshuur oo aqoonsan.",
        "Replace with the destination state agriculture / animal-health agency. Some species, breeds, or vaccinations have specific entry rules.": "Ku beddel hay'adda beeraha / caafimaadka xayawaanka ee gobolka aad u socotid. Jinsiyaadka qaarkood, noocyada, ama tallaaladu waxay leeyihiin qawaaniin gelitaan oo gaar ah.",
        "Replace with the destination state department of health URL.": "Ku beddel URL-ka waaxda caafimaadka ee gobolka aad u socotid.",
        "Replace with the destination state labor agency for paid leave, withholding, and labor law basics.": "Ku beddel hay'adda shaqaalaha ee gobolka aad u socotid ee fasaxa lacag-bixin leh, hayidda, iyo aasaaska sharciga shaqaalaha.",
        "Replace with the destination state's attorney general or housing agency. Local ordinances may add protections.": "Ku beddel xeer-ilaaliyaha guud ama hay'adda guryaha ee gobolka aad u socotid. Qaanuunnada deegaanku waxay ku dari karaan ilaalinno.",
        "Replace with the destination state's official tax agency website. Tax rules and forms change frequently.": "Ku beddel shabakadda hay'adda canshuurta rasmiga ah ee gobolka aad u socotid. Qawaaniinta canshuurta iyo foomamku waxay isbeddelaan si joogto ah.",
        "Replace with the destination state's professional licensing portal or relevant board for the specific profession.": "Ku beddel bogga shatiga xirfadda ee gobolka aad u socotid ama guddiga la xiriira xirfadda gaarka ah.",
        "Replace with the official NLC information page. Participation status and rules can change.": "Ku beddel bogga macluumaadka rasmiga ah ee NLC. Xaaladda ka qaybgalka iyo qawaaniintu way isbeddeli karaan.",
        "Replace with the official destination state board of nursing URL. Board rules govern eligibility and endorsement.": "Ku beddel URL rasmi ah oo Guddiga Kalkaalisada ee gobolka aad u socotid. Qawaaniinta guddiga waxay maamulayaan u qalmitaanka iyo aqoonsiga.",
        "Replace with the receiving school's residency or tuition classification page. School rules differ from state-agency rules.": "Ku beddel bogga degenaanshaha ama kala saaridda kharashka waxbarashada ee dugsiga la helay. Qawaaniinta dugsigu way ka kala duwan yihiin qawaaniinta hay'adda gobolka.",
        "Required documents for the application": "Dukumentiyada loo baahan yahay codsiga",
        "Required notice periods for ending a lease": "Muddooyinka ogeysiiska loo baahan yahay si loo joojiyo heshiiska kirada",
        "Requirements for License via Endorsement - International": "Shuruudaha Shatiga iyada oo loo marayo Aqoonsi - Caalami ah",
        "Reset all selections": "Dib u deji dhammaan doorashooyinka",
        "Reset progress": "Dib u deji horumarka",
        "Residency Requirements - State University System of Florida": "Shuruudaha Degenaanshaha - State University System of Florida",
        "Residency Status - California Franchise Tax Board": "Xaaladda Degenaanshaha - California Franchise Tax Board",
        "Residency can affect tuition, taxes, licensing, and benefits, and is determined by the relevant state agency, school, or tax authority - not by MoveSafe.": "Degenaanshahu wuxuu saamayn ku yeelan karaa kharashka waxbarashada, canshuuraha, shatiga, iyo manaafacaadyada, waxaana go'aamiya hay'adda gobolka, dugsiga, ama maamulka canshuurta ee la xiriira, ee ma aha MoveSafe.",
        "Residency, Establishment of for Tuition Purposes": "Degenaanshaha, Aasaaska ee Ujeeddooyinka Kharashka Waxbarashada",
        "Resources For Non-US Citizens": "Khayraadka ee Aan-Muwaadiniinta US-Ahayn",
        "Resources for Non-U.S. Citizens - Illinois Student Assistance Commission": "Khayraadka Aan-Muwaadiniinta U.S.-Ahayn - Illinois Student Assistance Commission",
        "Review destination-state lease and tenant basics": "Eeg aasaaska heshiiska kirada iyo kireystaha ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Review recommended": "Eegis ayaa lagula talinayaa",
        "Risk level: %@": "Heerka khatarta: %@",
        "Road trip": "Safar baabuur",
        "Rules around possession, documentation, and refills can differ across states and pharmacies.": "Qawaaniinta ku saabsan haysashada, dukumentiyada, iyo dib-u-buuxinta way kala duwanaan karaan gobollada iyo farmasiyada.",
        "Rules may differ substantially by jurisdiction, and MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in a specific situation.": "Sharciyadu way ka kala duwanaan karaan si weyn xukunka kasta, MoveSafe-na ma go'aamiyo in haysashada, gaadiidka, ama isticmaalku raacayaan sharciga xaalad gaar ah.",
        "Rules vary widely. Verify with official sources.": "Sharciyada way si weyn u kala duwan yihiin. Ku hubi ilaha rasmiga ah.",
        "SSA POMS RS 00204.010 Lawful Presence Payment Provisions": "SSA POMS RS 00204.010 Qodobada Lacag-bixinta ee Joogitaanka Sharciga",
        "SSA POMS section on the lawful presence framework that informs Medicare and other federal benefits.": "Qaybta SSA POMS ee qaab-dhismeedka joogitaanka sharciga oo wargeliya Medicare iyo manaafacaadyada kale ee federaalka.",
        "SSN or identity documentation requirements if applicable": "Shuruudaha SSN ama dukumentiyada aqoonsiga haddii ay khusayaan",
        "School / institution policy": "Siyaasadda dugsiga / hay'adda",
        "School or institution": "Dugsi ama hay'ad",
        "School residency / tuition classification policy": "Siyaasadda degenaanshaha dugsiga / kala saaridda kharashka waxbarashada",
        "School residency classification": "Kala saaridda degenaanshaha dugsiga",
        "School residency classification, immunization, student insurance, housing.": "Kala saaridda degenaanshaha dugsiga, tallaalka, caymiska ardayda, guryaha.",
        "School-level requirements can affect tuition classification, enrollment, and clinical participation.": "Shuruudaha heerka dugsiga ayaa saamayn ku yeelan kara kala saaridda kharashka waxbarashada, isdiiwaangelinta, iyo ka qaybgalka isbitaalka.",
        "School-specific clinical onboarding requirements": "Shuruudaha gelinta isbitaalka ee dugsi-gaarka ah",
        "Schools set their own residency, health-insurance, and immunization requirements separate from state-agency rules.": "Dugsiyadu waxay sameystaan shuruudahooda degenaansho, caymis caafimaad, iyo tallaal oo ka gooni ah qawaaniinta hay'adaha gobolka.",
        "Secondary reference": "Tixraac labaad",
        "Security deposit limits and return deadlines": "Xayiraadaha deebaajiga ammaanka iyo kama dambaysta soo celinta",
        "Security deposit limits, notice periods, eviction rules, and late-fee rules can differ between states and between cities.": "Xayiraadaha deebaajiga ammaanka, muddooyinka ogeysiiska, qawaaniinta saaridda, iyo qawaaniinta dib-u-dhaca lacagta way ka kala duwanaan karaan gobollada iyo magaalooyinka.",
        "Select a destination state.": "Dooro gobol aad u socotid.",
        "Select a purpose.": "Dooro ujeeddo.",
        "Select a purpose…": "Dooro ujeeddo…",
        "Select a state…": "Dooro gobol…",
        "Select an origin state.": "Dooro gobol aad ka soo kacaysid.",
        "Select at least one category.": "Dooro ugu yaraan hal qayb.",
        "Select one or more. You can change these later.": "Dooro hal ama ka badan. Waad bedeli kartaa kuwan goor dambe.",
        "Selective Service System FAQ page.": "Bogga FAQ ee Selective Service System.",
        "Selective Service System Frequently Asked Questions": "Selective Service System Su'aalaha Inta Badan La Iwedyiiyo",
        "Selective Service System PDF chart that lists categories and exceptions.": "Jaantuska PDF ee Selective Service System oo liis garaynaya qaybaha iyo marka laga reebay.",
        "Selective Service System Who Must Register Chart (PDF)": "Selective Service System Jaantuska Yaan Waajib ku tahay Inuu Isdiiwaangeliyo (PDF)",
        "Selective Service System Who Needs to Register": "Selective Service System Yaan U Baahan Inuu Isdiiwaangeliyo",
        "Selective Service System main Who Needs to Register page, with nonimmigrant exception language.": "Bogga ugu weyn ee Selective Service System ee 'Who Needs to Register', oo leh luqadda marka laga reebay aan-socdaal-doon ah.",
        "Selective Service System materials generally describe a Selective Service registration requirement for almost all men ages 18 through 25 living in the United States, with an exception for men who are in the United States on a current valid nonimmigrant visa while that status remains valid up to age 26.": "Qalabka Nidaamka Selective Service guud ahaan waxay qeexayaan shuruudda diiwaangelinta Selective Service ku dhowaad dhammaan ragga da'doodu u dhaxaysiiso 18 ilaa 25 ee ku nool Mareykanka, oo marka laga reebay ragga ku jira Mareykanka iyada oo ay haystaan fiise aan-socdaal-doon ah oo ansax ah halka xaaladdaasi ansax tahay ilaa da'da 26.",
        "Selective Service registration is a federal requirement for almost all males ages 18 through 25 in the United States, regardless of citizenship, and many states link license or ID applications to that registration.": "Diiwaangelinta Selective Service waa shuruud federaal oo loogu talagalay ku dhowaad dhammaan ragga da'doodu u dhaxaysiiso 18 ilaa 25 ee ku nool Mareykanka, iyada oo aan loo eegin muwaadinimada, gobollo badan ayaa ku xirta codsiyada shatiga ama aqoonsiga diiwaangelintaas.",
        "Setting up mail forwarding or updating a state license can give a false sense that the federal address record is current, while a pending USCIS case may still be sending notices to an old address.": "Dejinta hor-u-xareynta boostada ama cusboonaysiinta shati gobol waxay bixin kartaa dareen been ah oo ah in diiwaanka cinwaanka federaalku uu hadda yahay, halka kiis USCIS oo sugaya uu wali u diri karo ogeysiisyada cinwaan duug ah.",
        "Settings": "Goobaha",
        "Share checklist": "Wadaag liiska hubinta",
        "Short-to-medium term internship or co-op in another state.": "Tababar shaqo ama wadashaqayn gaaban-ilaa-dhexdhexaad oo gobol kale ah.",
        "Show high-risk categories separately": "Tus qaybaha khatar-sare leh si gooni ah",
        "Some checklist items use placeholder sources. Replace with official sources before relying on them.": "Cinwaanada qaarkood ee liiska hubintu waxay isticmaalaan ilo boos-haye ah. Ku beddel ilaha rasmiga ah ka hor inta aadan ku tiirsanaan.",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules.": "Cinwaano qaar laga yaabaa in si kala duwan loo nidaamiyo xudduudaha gobollada dhexdooda, waxayna ku lug yeelan karaan sharciga gobolka, qawaaniinta deegaanka, sharciga federaalka, ama qawaaniinta hay'adaha.",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in any specific situation. Verify directly with official sources and consult a licensed attorney or relevant agency if needed.": "Cinwaanno qaar laga yaabaa in si kala duwan loo nidaamiyo xudduudaha gobollada dhexdooda, waxayna ku lug yeelan karaan sharciga gobolka, qawaaniinta deegaanka, sharciga federaalka, ama qawaaniinta hay'adaha. MoveSafe ma go'aamiyo in haysashada, gaadiidka, ama isticmaalku raacayaan sharciga xaalad gaar ah oo kasta. Si toos ah uga hubi ilaha rasmiga ah oo la tasho qareen shati haysta ama hay'adda la xiriirta haddii loo baahdo.",
        "Some sources have not been verified recently. Check the official website before relying on them.": "Ilaha qaarkood lama hubin dhowaan. Hubi shabakadda rasmiga ah ka hor inta aadan ku tiirsanaan.",
        "Some states issue driver licenses or state IDs to nonimmigrant visa applicants on a shortened renewal cycle that tracks the I-94 or an underlying federal document, instead of the multi-year cycle used for citizens. Fees, renewal timing, and steps after a status extension can differ between origin and destination states.": "Gobollo qaarkood waxay siiyaan shatiyada darawalnimada ama aqoonsiyada gobolka codsadayaasha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah wareeg cusboonaysiin oo gaaban oo raaca I-94 ama dukumenti federaal oo hoosta yaal, halkii ay isticmaali lahaayeen wareegga-sano-badan ee muwaadiniinta. Lacagaha, wakhtiga cusboonaysiinta, iyo tallaabooyinka ka dib kordhinta xaaladda way kala duwanaan karaan u dhaxeeyo gobollada aad ka soo kacaysid iyo aad u socotid.",
        "Source not yet documented": "Isha weli lama duubin",
        "Source status: %@": "Xaaladda isha: %@",
        "Sources referenced in this checklist": "Ilaha lagu tixraacay liiskan hubinta",
        "Sources to verify only": "Ilaha aad u baahan tahay inaad hubiso oo keliya",
        "Sources:": "Ilaha:",
        "Sources: placeholder - verify with the relevant official agency.": "Ilaha: boos-haye - ku hubi hay'adda rasmiga ah ee la xiriirta.",
        "Stale or placeholder sources only": "Ilaha duugay ama boos-haye oo keliya",
        "Stale source": "Isha duugay",
        "Stale source warning": "Digniinta isha duugay",
        "Start fresh": "Bilow cusub",
        "Starting work at a new worksite outside the LCA's MSA without an amended petition can affect status maintenance, and the timing of the amended petition filing matters for when the worker can begin at the new location.": "Bilaabidda shaqada goob shaqo oo cusub oo ka baxsan MSA-da LCA-da iyada oo aan la haynin codsi-bedelan waxay saamayn ku yeelan kartaa sii-haynta xaaladda, wakhtiga gudbinta codsi-bedelanku waa muhiim wakhtiga uu shaqaaluhu bilaabi karo goobta cusub.",
        "State DMV document checklists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1 and similar) can differ from those used for U.S. citizens or lawful permanent residents. Accepted combinations of passport, visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, and I-797 or employer letter may vary, and some states ask for an SSN card or an SSA ineligibility letter.": "Liisaska dukumentiyada DMV-da gobolka ee codsadayaasha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1, iyo kuwa la mid ah) way ka kala duwanaan karaan kuwa loo isticmaalo muwaadiniinta U.S. ama deganayaasha joogto ah ee sharciga ah. Isku-darka la aqbalo ee baasaboorka, fiisaha, I-94, I-20 ama DS-2019, iyo I-797 ama warqadda shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada waxay kala duwanaan karaan, gobollo qaarna waxay weydiiyaan kaadhka SSN ama warqadda u-qalmi-la'aanta SSA.",
        "State University of New York Board of Trustees policy on residency for tuition purposes, including which visa categories can establish New York domicile. suny.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing state university system domain.": "Siyaasadda State University of New York Board of Trustees ee degenaanshaha ujeeddooyinka kharashka waxbarashada, oo ay ku jirto qaybaha fiisaha ee aasaasi kara domicile New York. suny.edu wuxuu soo celiyaa 403 codsiyada aan-browser-ahayn (Cloudflare); taasi waa been ah oo taban oo la yaqaan oo domain nidaamka jaamacadda gobolka ah.",
        "State filing requirements, part-year residency, remote work implications.": "Shuruudaha gudbinta gobolka, degenaanshaha qayb-sano, saamaynta shaqada fog.",
        "State grant and scholarship programs each have their own rules about whether non-citizen students may be considered, what application form (FAFSA, a state alternative, or an institutional form) is used, and what documentation is needed.": "Barnaamijyada deeqaha iyo deeqaha waxbarashada ee gobolka kasta wuxuu leeyahay qawaaniintiisa gaarka ah ku saabsan inay ardayda aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn lagu tixgalin karo, foomka codsiga (FAFSA, bedel gobol, ama foom hay'adeed) loo isticmaalo, iyo dukumentiyada loo baahan yahay.",
        "State labor law basics (paid sick leave, breaks, final pay rules)": "Aasaaska sharciga shaqaalaha gobolka (fasaxa jiro lacag-bixin leh, nasiino, qawaaniinta lacag-bixinta dambe)",
        "State law": "Sharciga gobolka",
        "State residency basics": "Aasaaska degenaanshaha gobolka",
        "State tax filing can apply even when income is earned remotely. Rules differ by state.": "Gudbinta canshuurta gobolku waxay khusayn kartaa xitaa marka dakhliga laga kasbado meel fog. Sharciyada way ka kala duwan yihiin xukunka kasta.",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. A person treated as a nonresident alien on the federal return may still be a resident, part-year resident, or nonresident for state purposes depending on domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors. States may or may not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "Degenaanshaha canshuurta gobolka waxa lagu go'aamiyaa qawaaniinta gobol kasta oo gaarka ah, oo laga yaabo inay ka kala duwan yihiin degenaanshaha canshuurta federaalka. Qof loola dhaqmo sida nonresident alien soo celinta federaalka ayaa weli noqon kara resident, part-year resident, ama nonresident ujeeddooyinka gobolka iyada oo ku xiran domicile, maalmaha joogitaanka jirka, goobta shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, iyo arrimo kale. Gobollada laga yaabo inay raacaan ama aanay raacin marka laga reebay heshiiska canshuurta dakhliga federaalka.",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. Domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors can each play a role.": "Degenaanshaha canshuurta gobolka waxa lagu go'aamiyaa qawaaniinta gobol kasta oo gaarka ah, oo laga yaabo inay ka kala duwan yihiin degenaanshaha canshuurta federaalka. Domicile-ka, maalmaha joogitaanka jirka, goobta shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, iyo arrimo kale ayaa middood doorka qaadan karta.",
        "State tax withholding, labor law basics, remote work considerations.": "Hayidda canshuurta gobolka, aasaaska sharciga shaqaalaha, tixgelinta shaqada fog.",
        "States and individual public colleges and universities use different tuition-classification rules for non-citizens, including how prior in-state high school attendance, current immigration status, and a parent's residency are considered.": "Gobollada iyo kuliyadaha iyo jaamacadaha dadweynaha shakhsi ahaaneed waxay isticmaalaan qawaaniin kala saaridda kharashka waxbarashada oo kala duwan ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn, oo ay ku jiraan sida loo tixgaliyo ka qaybgalka dugsiga sare ee gobolka, xaaladda hadda ee socdaalka, iyo degenaanshaha waalidka.",
        "States may require proof of identity, residency, lawful presence, school documents, or other paperwork.": "Gobolladu waxay u baahan karaan caddaynta aqoonsiga, degenaanshaha, joogitaanka sharciga, dukumentiyada dugsiga, ama waraaqo kale.",
        "Staying in another state temporarily without intending to become a resident.": "Joogitaan gobol kale si ku meel gaar ah iyada oo aan la doonayn in la noqdo degane.",
        "Student health insurance requirements": "Shuruudaha caymiska caafimaadka ardayda",
        "Student or temporary resident exceptions": "Marka laga reebo ardayda ama deganayaasha ku meel gaarka ah",
        "Student relocation": "Guuritaanka ardayda",
        "Students: Ensure Your Address is Correct in SEVIS": "Ardayda: Hubi In Cinwaankaaga Saxan Yahay SEVIS",
        "Study in the States Complete Transfer of F-1 SEVIS Record": "Study in the States Dhamaystir U Wareejinta Diiwaanka F-1 SEVIS",
        "Study in the States Ensure Your Address Is Correct in SEVIS": "Study in the States Hubi In Cinwaankaaga Saxan Yahay SEVIS",
        "Study in the States F-1 STEM Optional Practical Training Extension": "Study in the States F-1 STEM Kordhinta Tababar Ficil ah oo Ikhtiyaari ah",
        "Study in the States OPT Student Reporting Requirements": "Study in the States Shuruudaha Warbixinta Ardayga OPT",
        "Study in the States Personal Information SEVIS Help Hub": "Study in the States Macluumaadka Shakhsiga ee Xarunta Kaalmada SEVIS",
        "Study in the States When to Report Changes to Your DSO": "Study in the States Wakhtiga la Soo Sheego Isbeddellada DSO-gaaga",
        "Subleasing rules": "Qawaaniinta dib-u-kirayn",
        "TSA REAL ID FAQs page covering documentation for citizens and non-citizens.": "Bogga FAQ ee REAL ID TSA oo daboolaya dukumentiyada muwaadiniinta iyo aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn.",
        "TSA REAL ID overview page. Note: www.dhs.gov/real-id now redirects to TSA's REAL ID page.": "Bogga dulmar REAL ID ee TSA. Ogeysiis: www.dhs.gov/real-id hadda waxa loo wareejinayaa bogga REAL ID ee TSA.",
        "Tap to collapse": "Taabo si aad u laabto",
        "Tap to expand": "Taabo si aad u ballaariso",
        "Taxes / state filing awareness": "Canshuuraha / wacyigelinta gudbinta gobolka",
        "Temporary Visitor Driver's License": "Shatiga Darawalnimada Booqdaha Ku Meel Gaar ah",
        "Temporary permit availability": "Helitaanka oggolaanshaha ku meel gaarka ah",
        "Temporary stay": "Joogitaan ku meel gaar ah",
        "Texas Board of Nursing - Licensure - Endorsement Information": "Texas Board of Nursing - Shatiga - Macluumaadka Aqoonsiga",
        "Texas Board of Nursing - Licensure Eligibility": "Texas Board of Nursing - U Qalmitaanka Shatiga",
        "Texas Board of Nursing endorsement information page, relevant when moving from another state with a license.": "Bogga macluumaadka aqoonsiga Texas Board of Nursing, oo khusaya marka laga guurayo gobol kale oo shati leh.",
        "Texas Board of Nursing licensure eligibility page covering general requirements and documentation expectations.": "Bogga u qalmitaanka shatiga Texas Board of Nursing oo daboolaya shuruudaha guud iyo rajooyinka dukumentiyada.",
        "Texas Department of Public Safety driver license identification documentation page covering U.S. citizen and non-U.S. citizen applicants.": "Bogga dukumentiyada aqoonsiga shatiga darawalnimada ee Texas Department of Public Safety oo daboolaya codsadayaasha muwaadiniinta U.S. iyo aan-muwaadiniinta U.S.-ahayn.",
        "Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board page on residency for tuition purposes, including categories of nonimmigrant applicants and special pathways under the Texas Education Code.": "Bogga Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board oo ku saabsan degenaanshaha ujeeddooyinka kharashka waxbarashada, oo ay ku jiraan qaybaha codsadayaasha aan-socdaal-doon ah iyo waddooyinka gaarka ah ee Texas Education Code.",
        "The deadline for applying for a destination-state license": "Kama dambaysta codsashada shatiga gobolka aad u socotid",
        "This checklist is based on your selected categories and available source data. It may not include every requirement that applies to your situation.": "Liiskan hubintu wuxuu ku saleysan yahay qaybahaaga la doortay iyo xogta isaha ee la heli karo. Waxaa laga yaabaa inuusan ku jirin shuruud kasta oo khusayso xaaladdaada.",
        "This checklist is not a legal conclusion. Verify with official sources and consult a licensed professional where appropriate.": "Liiskan hubintu ma aha gunaanad sharci. Ku hubi ilaha rasmiga ah oo la tasho xirfadle shati haysta marka uu ku habboon yahay.",
        "This source has not been verified in more than a year. Treat as stale and verify directly with the official source.": "Isha tan lama xaqiijin in ka badan hal sano. U qaado mid duugay oo si toos ah uga hubi isha rasmiga ah.",
        "This source has not been verified in more than six months. Check the official website before relying on it.": "Isha tan lama xaqiijin in ka badan lix bilood. Hubi shabakadda rasmiga ah ka hor inta aadan ku tiirsanaan.",
        "This source was checked more than 90 days ago. Review recommended.": "Isha tan waxaa la baaray in ka badan 90 maalmood ka hor. Eegis ayaa lagula talinayaa.",
        "Title transfer process": "Habka u wareejinta lahaanshaha",
        "Total topics to verify: %d": "Wadarta mowduucyada la hubinayo: %d",
        "Travel documentation if flying with a pet": "Dukumentiyada safarka haddii la duulayo xayawaan guriga",
        "Treating an intra-MSA worksite change as a full new petition can create unnecessary cost and timing risk, while assuming portability rules apply without checking the MSA boundaries can lead to status questions later.": "U qaadashada isbeddelka goobta shaqada gudaha-MSA-da sida codsi cusub oo buuxa waxay abuuri kartaa kharash aan loo baahnayn iyo khatar wakhti, halka is malaynta in qawaaniinta guuraysasho ay khusayaan iyada oo aan la hubinin xudduudaha MSA ay horseedi karto su'aalo xaaladeed goor dambe.",
        "Treats high-risk categories with a \"Do not assume\" label": "Wuxuu u qaadaa qaybaha khatar-sare leh calaamadda \"Ha is malayn\"",
        "Try clearing risk filters or the high-risk / stale-source toggles.": "Isku day inaad nadiifiso sifeeyayaasha khatarta ama beddelka khatar-sare / isha-duugay.",
        "USCIS AR-11 Alien's Change of Address Card": "USCIS AR-11 Kaadhka Isbeddelka Cinwaanka ee Aliens",
        "USCIS Employment Authorization page providing background on the EAD (Form I-766) used in some state DMV and licensing document lists.": "Bogga USCIS Employment Authorization oo bixiya macluumaad asal ah oo ku saabsan EAD (Foomka I-766) oo loo isticmaalay liisaska dukumentiyada DMV-da gobolka iyo shatiga qaarkood.",
        "USCIS Final Guidance on When to File an Amended or New H-1B Petition After Matter of Simeio Solutions LLC": "USCIS Hagidda Kama Dambaysta ah ee Wakhtiga la Gudbinayo Codsi-bedelan ama Codsi H-1B Cusub ka Dib Matter of Simeio Solutions LLC",
        "USCIS Form AR-11 PDF": "USCIS Foomka AR-11 PDF",
        "USCIS H-1B Specialty Occupations Landing Page": "Bogga Aasaasiga ah ee USCIS H-1B Specialty Occupations",
        "USCIS How to Change Your Address": "USCIS Sida loo Bedelo Cinwaankaaga",
        "USCIS L-1A Intracompany Transferee Executive or Manager": "USCIS L-1A U Wareeg Shirkadda Gudaheeda Maamule ama Maamule",
        "USCIS L-1A classification page.": "Bogga kala saaridda USCIS L-1A.",
        "USCIS L-1B Intracompany Transferee Specialized Knowledge": "USCIS L-1B U Wareeg Shirkadda Gudaheeda Aqoonta Takhasuska",
        "USCIS L-1B classification page.": "Bogga kala saaridda USCIS L-1B.",
        "USCIS Launches New Online Change of Address Tool": "USCIS Wuxuu Bilaabay Qalabka Cusub ee Cinwaan-bedelka Onlaynka",
        "USCIS O-1 Visa Individuals with Extraordinary Ability or Achievement": "USCIS O-1 Fiisaha Shakhsiyaadka leh Awood ama Guul Aan Caadi Ahayn",
        "USCIS O-1 classification page.": "Bogga kala saaridda USCIS O-1.",
        "USCIS Policy Manual Volume 1 Part A Chapter 10 Changes of Address": "USCIS Policy Manual Mug 1 Qaybta A Cutubka 10 Isbeddelka Cinwaanka",
        "USCIS Policy Manual chapter that describes federal address-change reporting.": "Cutubka USCIS Policy Manual oo qeexaya warbixinta isbeddelka cinwaanka federaalka.",
        "USCIS archive page summarizing the 2015 Simeio Solutions final guidance and the LCA-amendment trigger for worksite changes outside the MSA.": "Bogga kaydka USCIS oo kooba hagidda kama dambaysta ah ee Simeio Solutions 2015 iyo kicinta beddelka LCA ee isbeddelka goobta shaqada ee ka baxsan MSA.",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that a U.S. Postal Service change-of-address request does not change a record with USCIS and that USPS does not forward USCIS mail. A destination-state DMV address update is also a separate step from the federal AR-11 filing.": "Hagidda USCIS guud ahaan waxay tilmaamaysaa in codsiga cinwaan-bedelka Adeegga Boostada Mareykanka uusan bedelin diiwaanka USCIS iyo in USPS uusan hor u xarayn boostada USCIS. Cusboonaysiinta cinwaanka DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid sidoo kale waa tallaabo gooni ah laga gudbinta AR-11 ee federaalka.",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that an H-1B worker moving to a new worksite within the same MSA or area of intended employment as the existing LCA does not require a new LCA or an amended H-1B petition, although the existing LCA may still need to be posted at the new worksite. The federal AR-11 address change requirement still applies to the worker.": "Hagidda USCIS guud ahaan waxay tilmaamaysaa in shaqaale H-1B ah oo u guuraya goob shaqo oo cusub oo ku jirta MSA isku mid ah ama aagga shaqada loogu talagalay sida LCA-da hadda jirta uu uga baahnayn LCA cusub ama codsi-bedelan H-1B, in kasta oo LCA-da hadda jirta wali laga yaabo inay u baahan tahay in lagu daabaco goobta shaqo ee cusub. Shuruudda isbeddelka cinwaanka AR-11 ee federaalka wali waxay khusayso shaqaalaha.",
        "USCIS newsroom alert describing the online change-of-address tool and clarifying that USPS forwarding does not change a USCIS record.": "Ogeysiis qol-warkaad USCIS oo qeexaya qalabka cinwaan-bedelka onlaynka oo cadeynaya in hor-u-xareynta USPS uusan bedelin diiwaanka USCIS.",
        "USCIS umbrella page on the federal change-of-address requirement, including the online change-of-address tool.": "Bogga guud ee USCIS oo ku saabsan shuruudda isbeddelka cinwaanka federaalka, oo ay ku jirto qalabka cinwaan-bedelka onlaynka.",
        "USPS Mail Forwarding / Change of Address": "USPS Hor-u-xareyn Boostada / Isbeddelka Cinwaanka",
        "USPS mail-forwarding page; referenced to clarify that USPS change-of-address does not substitute for federal AR-11 filing per USCIS guidance.": "Bogga hor-u-xareynta boostada USPS; waxa loo tixraacay si loo caddeeyo in cinwaan-bedelka USPS uusan beddelin gudbinta AR-11 ee federaalka sida hagidda USCIS.",
        "Under 22 CFR Part 62, J-1 program sponsors maintain the SEVIS record and monitor the site of activity for each exchange visitor. A move that changes residence, site of activity, or host organization generally triggers an exchange-visitor reporting obligation to the sponsor and a sponsor update to SEVIS.": "Sida 22 CFR Qaybta 62, kafiilada barnaamijka J-1 waxay sii-haystaan diiwaanka SEVIS waxayna kormeeraan goobta howsha ee booqde kasta oo is-weydaarsi. U guuritaan bedeli degenaanshaha, goobta howsha, ama hay'adda hoy-yaha ah ee guud ahaan kicinaysa waajibka warbixin booqde is-weydaarsi kafiilka iyo cusboonaysiin kafiil ee SEVIS.",
        "Under USCIS guidance following Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), an H-1B worker's move to a worksite outside the metropolitan statistical area (MSA) or area of intended employment listed on the current Labor Condition Application (LCA) is generally a material change that calls for a new LCA and an amended H-1B petition.": "Sida hagidda USCIS ee ka dib Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), u guuritaanka shaqaalaha H-1B goob shaqo oo ka baxsan aagga tirakoobka magaaladda (MSA) ama aagga shaqada loogu talagalay ee ku qoran Codsiga Shuruudaha Shaqaalaha hadda (LCA) guud ahaan waa isbeddel muhiim ah oo loo baahan yahay LCA cusub iyo codsi-bedelan H-1B.",
        "Understand how the destination state defines residency": "Faham sida gobolka aad u socotid uu u qeexo degenaanshaha",
        "University of California admissions page on the AB 540 nonresident tuition exemption, noting that most nonimmigrant visa holders such as F-1 or J-1 generally cannot establish California residency for tuition purposes.": "Bogga gelitaanka University of California ee ku saabsan ka-saaridda kharashka waxbarashada nonresident ee AB 540, oo tilmaamaya in inta badan haystayaasha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah sida F-1 ama J-1 guud ahaan aanay aasaasi karin degenaanshaha California ujeeddooyinka kharashka waxbarashada.",
        "Update employment paperwork and state tax forms": "Cusboonaysii waraaqaha shaqada iyo foomamka canshuurta gobolka",
        "Use do not assume language. Do not state that USPS or DMV updates can substitute for AR-11 (USCIS guidance says they generally do not). Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "U isticmaal luqadda 'ha is malayn'. Ha sheegin in cusboonaysiinada USPS ama DMV ay beddeli karaan AR-11 (hagidda USCIS waxay tiraahdaa guud ahaan ma sameeyaan). Ka fogow liiska iOS SafeCopy ee laga fogaado (luqadda gunaanad sharci iyo luqadda ka fogaanshaha ciqaabta).",
        "Vaccination, licensing, breed restrictions, housing pet policies.": "Tallaalka, shatiga, xayiraadaha nooca, siyaasadaha xayawaanka guriga ee guriga.",
        "Vaccination, local licensing, breed restrictions, and landlord pet policies can vary across destination states and cities.": "Tallaalka, shatiga deegaanka, xayiraadaha nooca, iyo siyaasadaha xayawaanka guriga ee mulkiilaha guriga way kala duwanaan karaan gobollada iyo magaalooyinka aad u socotid.",
        "Vehicle registration": "Diiwaangelinta baabuurka",
        "Vehicle registration rules can change after a state-to-state move, especially if the destination state treats you as a new resident.": "Qawaaniinta diiwaangelinta baabuurka way isbeddeli karaan ka dib guuritaan gobol-ka-gobol, gaar ahaan haddii gobolka aad u socotid uu ku tixgaliyo degane cusub.",
        "Verification progress": "Horumarka hubinta",
        "Verified: %1$d of %2$d": "La xaqiijiyay: %1$d ka mid ah %2$d",
        "Verify ACA marketplace categories described as lawfully present for nonimmigrants": "Hubi qaybaha suuqa ACA ee loo qeexay joogitaan sharci ah ee aan-socdaal-doon ah",
        "Verify F-1 SEVIS school-transfer steps if the move is to a different school": "Hubi tallaabooyinka u wareejinta dugsiga SEVIS ee F-1 haddii guuritaanku yahay dugsi kale",
        "Verify FICA (Social Security and Medicare) handling for F-1 and J-1 nonresident aliens": "Hubi qaabilaadda FICA (Social Security iyo Medicare) ee F-1 iyo J-1 nonresident aliens",
        "Verify H-1B portability and address handling for a move within the same MSA": "Hubi guuraysasho H-1B iyo qaabilaadda cinwaanka ee guuritaanka MSA isku mid ah",
        "Verify J-1 program sponsor reporting for site-of-activity or host-organization changes": "Hubi warbixinta kafiilka barnaamijka J-1 ee isbeddelka goobta-howsha ama hay'adda hoy-yaha ah",
        "Verify L-1 or O-1 worksite change handling against the approved petition": "Hubi qaabilaadda isbeddelka goobta shaqada L-1 ama O-1 marka loo barbar dhigo codsiga la oggolaaday",
        "Verify Medicare and Medicaid eligibility rules that may apply to nonimmigrants after a move": "Hubi qawaaniinta u qalmitaanka Medicare iyo Medicaid ee laga yaabo inay khusayaan aan-socdaal-doon ah ka dib guuritaanka",
        "Verify SEVP Portal updates for address, employer, and unemployment-day tracking on OPT or STEM OPT": "Hubi cusboonaysiinada SEVP Portal ee cinwaanka, shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, iyo la-socoshada maalmaha shaqo-la'aanta ee OPT ama STEM OPT",
        "Verify destination Board of Nursing documentation for non-citizen applicants": "Hubi dukumentiyada Guddiga Kalkaalisada ee aad u socotid ee codsadayaasha aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn",
        "Verify destination-state DMV documents for non-citizen applicants": "Hubi dukumentiyada DMV ee gobolka aad u socotid ee codsadayaasha aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn",
        "Verify destination-state DMV documents for nonimmigrant visa applicants": "Hubi dukumentiyada DMV ee gobolka aad u socotid ee codsadayaasha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah",
        "Verify destination-state financial aid eligibility rules for non-citizens": "Hubi qawaaniinta u qalmitaanka kaalmada maaliyadeed ee gobolka aad u socotid ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn",
        "Verify destination-state professional licensing documentation rules for visa or OPT applicants": "Hubi qawaaniinta dukumentiyada shatiga xirfadda ee gobolka aad u socotid ee codsadayaasha fiise ama OPT",
        "Verify destination-state tuition classification rules for non-citizen students": "Hubi qawaaniinta kala saaridda kharashka waxbarashada ee gobolka aad u socotid ee ardayda aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn",
        "Verify destination-state tuition classification rules for nonimmigrant visa students": "Hubi qawaaniinta kala saaridda kharashka waxbarashada ee gobolka aad u socotid ee ardayda fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah",
        "Verify documentation a destination-state licensing board requires for non-citizens": "Hubi dukumentiyada uu guddiga shatiga gobolka aad u socotid uu uga baahan yahay aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn",
        "Verify dual-status year considerations for the federal return covering a move": "Hubi tixgelinta sannadka xaaladda labanlaha ah ee soo celinta federaalka ee daboolaysa guuritaanka",
        "Verify federal tax residency under the Substantial Presence Test after a move": "Hubi degenaanshaha canshuurta federaalka hoos imanaysa Substantial Presence Test ka dib guuritaanka",
        "Verify health-insurance marketplace options in the destination state": "Hubi doorashooyinka suuqa caymiska caafimaadka ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Verify how Selective Service registration applies to a specific nonimmigrant status": "Hubi sida diiwaangelinta Selective Service ay ugu khusayso xaalad aan-socdaal-doon ah oo gaar ah",
        "Verify how a destination-state REAL ID expiration may track an underlying federal document": "Hubi sida dhicitaanka REAL ID ee gobolka aad u socotid uu uga raaci karo dukumenti federaal oo hoosta yaal",
        "Verify how the federal five-year waiting period applies in the destination state": "Hubi sida muddada sugitaanka shanta sano ee federaalku ay ugu khusayso gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Verify license fee and renewal-cycle rules that may follow an I-94 expiration": "Hubi qawaaniinta lacagta shatiga iyo wareegga-cusboonaysiinta ee laga yaabo inay raacaan dhicitaanka I-94",
        "Verify rules for transporting prescription medication across state lines": "Hubi qawaaniinta gaadiidka dawada dhakhtarku qoray xudduudaha gobollada dhexdooda",
        "Verify soon": "Dhowaan hubi",
        "Verify state tax residency and filing rules after a move": "Hubi degenaanshaha canshuurta gobolka iyo qawaaniinta gudbinta ka dib guuritaanka",
        "Verify state tax residency rules and how they interact with federal nonresident alien status": "Hubi qawaaniinta degenaanshaha canshuurta gobolka iyo sida ay ula falgashaan xaaladda nonresident alien ee federaalka",
        "Verify state-funded benefit programs that may apply during a federal waiting period": "Hubi barnaamijyada manaafacaadka lacag-gobol leh ee laga yaabo inay khusayaan inta lagu jiro muddada sugitaanka federaalka",
        "Verify the 10-day DSO or sponsor SEVIS address update for F-1 and J-1 status": "Hubi cusboonaysiinta cinwaanka SEVIS ee DSO ama kafiilka 10-maalmood ah ee xaaladda F-1 iyo J-1",
        "Verify the 10-day USCIS address change filing after an interstate move": "Hubi gudbinta isbeddelka cinwaanka USCIS ee 10-maalmood ah ka dib u guuritaanka gobol-dhaafka ah",
        "Verify the destination-state driver's license deadline": "Hubi kama dambaysta shatiga darawalnimada ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Verify vehicle registration requirements after moving": "Hubi shuruudaha diiwaangelinta baabuurka ka dib guuritaanka",
        "Verify whether an H-1B amended petition is needed for a worksite move to a new MSA": "Hubi inay codsi-bedelan H-1B loo baahan yahay guuritaanka goobta shaqada ee MSA cusub",
        "Verify whether to apply for a REAL ID or a standard credential": "Hubi inaad codsato REAL ID ama aqoonsi caadi ah",
        "Version": "Nooca",
        "View example checklist": "Eeg liiska hubinta tusaalaha ah",
        "WHAT TO VERIFY": "WAA MAXAY WAXA AAD U BAAHAN TAHAY INAAD HUBISO",
        "WHY THIS MATTERS": "WAA MAXAY SABABTA TANI U MUHIIM TAHAY",
        "Washington Department of Licensing proof-of-identity page including non-citizen documents such as I-551 annotations and U.S. visa stamps.": "Bogga caddaynta aqoonsiga ee Washington Department of Licensing oo ay ku jiraan dukumentiyada aan-muwaadin sida xashiyaha I-551 iyo shaamadaha fiisaha U.S.",
        "What MoveSafe does": "Waxa MoveSafe sameeyo",
        "What MoveSafe does not do": "Waxa MoveSafe aanu samayn",
        "What confirmation record (receipt, screenshot, mailed copy) to keep after filing": "Diiwaan xaqiijin (rasiid, sawir-shaashad, nuqul-boosto) ee la hayo ka dib gudbinta",
        "What documentation, if any, the DMV keeps if a non-citizen declines": "Dukumenti kasta, haddii ay jirto, ee DMV-da haysato haddii aan-muwaadin uu diido",
        "What documents (for example, EAD, transcripts, affidavits, tax records) the registrar requires to support a tuition-classification request": "Dukumentiyada (tusaale, EAD, koobiyaha buugaagta, dhaariyo qoraal ah, diiwaanada canshuurta) ee diiwaangeluhu uu uga baahan yahay si loo taageero codsi kala saarid kharashka waxbarashada",
        "What documents (for example, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, transcripts, affidavits, tax records) the registrar requires to support a classification request": "Dukumentiyada (tusaale, I-94, I-20 ama DS-2019, I-797, koobiyaha buugaagta, dhaariyo qoraal ah, diiwaanada canshuurta) ee diiwaangeluhu uu uga baahan yahay si loo taageero codsi kala saarid",
        "What tax or residency documentation the state aid agency requires": "Dukumentiyada canshuurta ama degenaanshaha ee hay'adda kaalmada gobolku uu uga baahan yahay",
        "What to verify:": "Waxa la hubinayo:",
        "Whether AR-11 has been filed separately with USCIS within the federal 10-day window": "Inay AR-11 si gooni ah loogu gudbiyay USCIS muddada 10-maalmood ee federaalka",
        "Whether DACA recipients are currently considered for marketplace coverage, since this category has changed at the federal level": "Inay DACA-hayayaasha hadda lagu tixgaliyo caymiska suuqa, maaddaama qaybtan ay ku bedeshay heerka federaalka",
        "Whether Medicaid or state marketplace rules differ": "Inay qawaaniinta Medicaid ama suuqa gobolku kala duwan yihiin",
        "Whether REAL ID and standard (non-REAL-ID) credentials use different document checklists": "Inay aqoonsiyada REAL ID iyo caadiga ah (aan-REAL-ID ahayn) ay isticmaalaan liisas dukumenti oo kala duwan",
        "Whether REAL ID requirements apply for your situation": "Inay shuruudaha REAL ID khusayaan xaaladdaada",
        "Whether USPS mail forwarding is in place for the new address": "Inay hor-u-xareynta boostada USPS-ga ay diyaar u tahay cinwaanka cusub",
        "Whether a Social Security card or an SSA ineligibility letter is required to apply": "Inay loo baahan yahay kaadhka Social Security ama warqadda u-qalmi-la'aanta SSA si loo codsado",
        "Whether a USPS change-of-address forwards mail from USCIS (USCIS guidance generally indicates it does not)": "Inay USPS-ga cinwaan-bedelku uu hor u xareeyo boostada ka soo socota USCIS (hagidda USCIS guud ahaan waxay tilmaamaysaa inaanay sameynin)",
        "Whether a change in site of activity or host organization needs prior sponsor authorization before it occurs": "Inay isbeddel goobta howsha ama hay'adda hoy-yaha ah uu uga baahan yahay oggolaansho hore oo kafiil ka hor inta uu dhicin",
        "Whether a closer connection exception or a tax-treaty tie-breaker rule may apply": "Inay marka laga reebo xidhiidh dhowaad ama qaanuun heshiis-canshuureed-jabin laga yaabo inay khusayso",
        "Whether a first-year choice or a tax-treaty election can change the analysis": "Inay doorashada sannadka koowaad ama doorashada heshiis-canshuureed ay bedeli karto falanqaynta",
        "Whether a fresh I-94 printout or an updated I-797 is needed at the time of renewal, and whether the DMV verifies status through a federal system in real time": "Inay daabacaad I-94 oo cusub ama I-797 la cusboonaysiiyay loo baahan yahay wakhtiga cusboonaysiinta, iyo inay DMV-du xaqiijiso xaaladda iyada oo loo marayo nidaam federaal wakhti dhab ah",
        "Whether a license issued to a non-citizen may have a renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "Inay shatiga loo bixiyo aan-muwaadin ah uu yeelan karo wareeg cusboonaysiin oo xidhan dukumenti federaal",
        "Whether a license issued to a non-citizen may have a shorter renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "Inay shatiga loo bixiyo aan-muwaadin ah uu yeelan karo wareeg cusboonaysiin oo gaaban oo xidhan dukumenti federaal",
        "Whether a license issued to a visa holder may have a shorter renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "Inay shatiga loo bixiyo hayste fiise uu yeelan karo wareeg cusboonaysiin oo gaaban oo xidhan dukumenti federaal",
        "Whether a move that includes a change of school or program site requires additional SEVIS steps beyond an address update": "Inay u guuritaan ay ku jirto isbeddel dugsi ama goob barnaamij uu uga baahan yahay tallaabooyin SEVIS oo dheeri ah ka sokow cusboonaysiinta cinwaanka",
        "Whether a move triggers a special enrollment period and what documents the marketplace requires to verify status": "Inay u guuritaanku uu kicinayo muddada isdiiwaangelinta gaarka ah iyo dukumentiyada uu suuqu uga baahan yahay xaqiijinta xaaladda",
        "Whether a new Form I-20 from the destination school has been issued and signed": "Inay Foomka I-20 cusub oo ka yimid dugsiga aad u socotid la bixiyay oo la saxiixay",
        "Whether a new application is required": "Inay codsi cusub loo baahan yahay",
        "Whether a separate identifier or marking appears on credentials issued to applicants with temporary lawful status in that state": "Inay aqoonsi gooni ah ama calaamadayn ay ka muuqato aqoonsiyada loo bixiyo codsadayaasha xaalad sharci ku meel gaar ah haysta gobolkaas",
        "Whether a short-term placement exception (subject to federal time limits) applies before an amendment is needed": "Inay marka laga reebo meelaynta muddo-gaaban (oo lagu xaddiday wakhtiyada federaalka) khusayso ka hor inta aan beddel loo baahan",
        "Whether a standard (non-REAL-ID) credential is offered as an alternative": "Inay aqoonsi caadi ah (aan-REAL-ID ahayn) loo bixiyo bedel ahaan",
        "Whether a standard (non-REAL-ID) credential is offered as an alternative and whether its expiration is also tied to a federal document": "Inay aqoonsi caadi ah (aan-REAL-ID ahayn) loo bixinayo bedel ahaan iyo inay dhicitaankiisa sidoo kale ku xidhan yahay dukumenti federaal",
        "Whether a state return for the destination or origin state must be filed alongside the federal dual-status return": "Inay soo celinta gobol ee gobolka aad u socotid ama ka soo kacaysid ay tahay in la gudbiyo dhinaca soo celinta federaalka ee xaaladda labanlaha ah",
        "Whether a student is classified as in-state, out-of-state, or under a tuition-equity policy can change the cost of attendance significantly, and rules can differ between the state higher-education agency, a state university system, and individual institutions.": "Inay arday loo kala saaro gobol-gudaha, gobol-dibadda, ama hoos timaad siyaasadda sinaanta kharashka waxbarashada waxay si weyn u bedeli kartaa kharashka ka qaybgalka, qawaaniinaha way ka kala duwanaan karaan hay'adda waxbarashada sare ee gobolka, nidaamka jaamacadda gobolka, iyo hay'adaha shaqsiyeed.",
        "Whether a student is classified as resident, nonresident, or under a state tuition-equity provision can change the cost of attendance significantly, and rules vary across origin and destination states and across institutions within a state.": "Inay arday loo kala saaro resident, nonresident, ama hoos timaad qodobka sinaanta kharashka waxbarashada ee gobolka waxay si weyn u bedeli kartaa kharashka ka qaybgalka, qawaaniinaha way ka kala duwan yihiin gobollada aad ka soo kacaysid iyo aad u socotid iyo hay'adaha gobolka gudahiisa.",
        "Whether a year of transition to resident-alien status under the Substantial Presence Test changes FICA treatment": "Inay sannadka u kala-guurka xaaladda resident-alien hoos imanaysa Substantial Presence Test uu bedelo qaabka FICA",
        "Whether an SSN is required to apply, and whether an ITIN, an SSA ineligibility letter, or an affidavit is accepted as an alternative": "Inay SSN loo baahan yahay si loo codsado, iyo inay ITIN, warqadda u-qalmi-la'aanta SSA, ama dhaariyo qoraal ah loo aqbalo bedel ahaan",
        "Whether an exempt-individual rule (for certain F, J, M, Q categories) may apply and for how many years": "Inay qaanuun shaqsi-laga-reebay (qaybaha F, J, M, Q qaarkood) uu khusayn karo iyo immisa sano",
        "Whether any active USCIS receipt number has its own e-Notification or online-account address that needs to be checked": "Inay nambar rasiidh USCIS oo firfircoon uu leeyahay e-Ogeysiis ama cinwaan xisaab onlayn oo loo baahan yahay in la hubiyo",
        "Whether any category-specific rules (research scholar, professor, intern, trainee, physician, au pair, and others) add steps that the sponsor must approve": "Inay qawaaniin qayb-gaar ah (cilmi-baare, professorka, tababar, tababaran, dhakhtarka, au pair, iyo kuwa kale) ku daraan tallaabooyin uu kafiilku waa inuu oggolaado",
        "Whether any change in job duties, hours, or wage triggers a separate amendment analysis even when the worksite stays in the same MSA": "Inay isbeddel kasta oo waajibaadka shaqada, saacadaha, ama mushaharka uu kicinayo falanqayn beddel oo gooni ah xitaa marka goobta shaqadu ay ku sii jiro MSA isku mid ah",
        "Whether any pending USCIS case (I-129, I-485, I-765, I-130, and similar) requires a separate address update beyond AR-11": "Inay kiis kasta oo USCIS oo sugaya (I-129, I-485, I-765, I-130, iyo kuwa la mid ah) uu uga baahan yahay cusboonaysiin cinwaan oo gooni ah ka sokow AR-11",
        "Whether any state credit programs (for example, an earned-income or family credit) consider non-citizen filers": "Inay barnaamijyada amaahda gobol (tusaale, dakhli-kasban ama amaahda qoyska) ay tixgaliyaan filerada aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn",
        "Whether benefits use by certain immigrant categories can interact with future immigration filings, and whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before applying": "Inay isticmaalka manaafacaadka ee qaybaha qaar ka mid ah soogalootigu uu la falgalo gudbinta socdaalka mustaqbalka, iyo inay tahay inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor codsiga",
        "Whether both physical and mailing addresses are recorded in SEVIS if they differ": "Inay labadaba cinwaanka jirka iyo boostada lagu duubay SEVIS haddii ay kala duwan yihiin",
        "Whether clinicals can begin before full licensure": "Inay xilliyada isbitaalka bilaaban karaan ka hor shatiga buuxa",
        "Whether destination-state Medicaid offers emergency-only coverage to nonimmigrants and what documentation it requires": "Inay Medicaid-ka gobolka aad u socotid uu bixinayo caymis degdeg-keliya ee aan-socdaal-doon ah iyo dukumentiyada uu uga baahan yahay",
        "Whether documentation (original container, prescription) is recommended": "Inay dukumentiyada (weelka asalka, dawada dhakhtarku qoray) lagula talinayo",
        "Whether employer name, address, supervisor, and start or end dates are current in the SEVP Portal or reported to the DSO": "Inay magaca shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, cinwaanka, kormeeruhu, iyo taariikhaha bilaabista ama dhamaadku ay hadda ku jiraan SEVP Portal ama loo sheegay DSO-ga",
        "Whether federal rules apply to interstate transportation": "Inay qawaaniinta federaalku khusayaan gaadiidka gobol-dhaafka ah",
        "Whether high school attendance or graduation in the destination state is one of the qualifying paths": "Inay ka qaybgalka ama qalin-jabinta dugsiga sare ee gobolka aad u socotid ay yihiin mid ka mid ah jidadka u qalma",
        "Whether identity, residency, and SSN documents are required in addition to status documents": "Inay dukumentiyada aqoonsiga, degenaanshaha, iyo SSN loo baahan yahay ka sokow dukumentiyada xaaladda",
        "Whether immigration status or school documents affect the process": "Inay xaaladda socdaalka ama dukumentiyada dugsiga saamayn ku yeeshaan habka",
        "Whether institutional aid at your destination school is governed by separate rules from state aid": "Inay kaalmada hay'adda ee dugsigaaga aad u socotid lagu maamulo qawaaniin ka gooni ah kaalmada gobolka",
        "Whether internationally educated nurses must complete a credentials-evaluation step (for example, CGFNS)": "Inay kalkaalisada caalami ah waxbarashada laga qaadayo ay tahay inay dhammeystiraan tallaabada qiimaynta aqoonsiga (tusaale, CGFNS)",
        "Whether local ordinances are stricter than state rules": "Inay qaanuunada deegaanku ay aad uga adag yihiin qawaaniinta gobolka",
        "Whether local taxes apply": "Inay canshuuraha deegaanku khusayaan",
        "Whether local tenant protections apply": "Inay ilaalinta kireystaha ee deegaanku khusayso",
        "Whether moving mid-coverage requires reapplication in the destination state": "Inay u guuritaanka bartamaha caymisku uu uga baahan yahay dib-u-codsasho gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Whether moving mid-program changes the classification timeline": "Inay u guuritaanka dhexda barnaamijka uu bedelo wakhtiga kala saaridda",
        "Whether out-of-state students need special documentation": "Inay ardayda aan-gobolka-ahayn u baahan yihiin dukumentiyo gaar ah",
        "Whether part-year residency rules apply": "Inay qawaaniinta degenaanshaha qayb-sano khusayaan",
        "Whether pending discipline or incomplete education affects transfer": "Inay edbinta lasoo gudbiyey ama waxbarashada aan dhammaystirnayn ay saamayn ku yeeshaan u wareejinta",
        "Whether permits, age restrictions, documentation, or location-specific rules apply": "Inay oggolaanshooyinka, xayiraadaha da'da, dukumentiyada, ama qawaaniinta meel-gaarka ah ay khusayaan",
        "Whether posting requirements for the existing LCA at the new location, when in the same MSA, have been satisfied": "Inay shuruudaha boggaaga LCA-da hadda ee goobta cusub, marka ay tahay MSA isku mid ah, la buuxiyay",
        "Whether premium tax credit or cost-sharing reduction eligibility rules have changed for the relevant year": "Inay qawaaniinta u qalmitaanka amaahda canshuurta premium ama dhimista wadaagga kharashku ay isbeddeleen sannadka la xiriira",
        "Whether prescriptions can be transferred": "Inay dawooyinka la wareejin karo",
        "Whether professional legal advice is needed": "Inay talo xirfadeed oo sharci loo baahan yahay",
        "Whether proof of in-state residency is needed in addition to identity and status documents": "Inay caddaynta degenaanshaha gobolka loo baahan yahay ka sokow dukumentiyada aqoonsiga iyo xaaladda",
        "Whether proof of in-state residency is required in addition to identity and status documents, and what residency proofs the DMV accepts for new arrivals": "Inay caddaynta degenaanshaha gobolka loo baahan yahay ka sokow dukumentiyada aqoonsiga iyo xaaladda, iyo caddaymaha degenaanshaha uu DMV-du u aqbalo soo gaarayaasha cusub",
        "Whether remote work creates state tax or payroll issues": "Inay shaqada fog ay abuurto arrimaha canshuurta gobolka ama mushaharka",
        "Whether remote work may create tax issues": "Inay shaqada fog ay abuuri karto arrimaha canshuurta",
        "Whether renewal fees and step counts differ from the standard renewal process used for citizens": "Inay lacagaha cusboonaysiinta iyo tirinta tallaabooyinku ay ka kala duwan yihiin habka cusboonaysiinta caadiga ah ee loo isticmaalo muwaadiniinta",
        "Whether residency affects tuition, taxes, licenses, or benefits": "Inay degenaanshuhu uu saamayn ku yeesho kharashka waxbarashada, canshuuraha, shatiyada, ama manaafacaadyada",
        "Whether school attendance affects residency": "Inay ka qaybgalka dugsigu uu saamayn ku yeesho degenaanshaha",
        "Whether school attendance affects tax residency": "Inay ka qaybgalka dugsigu uu saamayn ku yeesho degenaanshaha canshuurta",
        "Whether specific state grants or scholarships consider DACA recipients or lawful permanent residents in their eligibility criteria": "Inay deeqaha ama deeqaha waxbarashada gobol gaar ah ay tixgaliyaan DACA-hayayaasha ama deganayaasha joogto ah ee sharciga ah shuruudaha u qalmitaanka",
        "Whether state-specific uninsured/underinsured motorist rules apply": "Inay qawaaniinta darawalka aan-caymisan/yaraan-caymisan ee gobolka u gaarka ah khusayaan",
        "Whether student health insurance is required": "Inay caymiska caafimaadka ardayda loo baahan yahay",
        "Whether students or temporary residents are treated differently": "Inay ardayda ama deganayaasha ku meel gaarka ah si kala duwan loo qaado",
        "Whether temporary practice permits exist": "Inay jiraan oggolaanshooyin dhaqan ku meel gaar ah",
        "Whether the 10-day clock starts on the move date or the date the new address becomes permanent": "Inay saacadda 10-maalmood ay ka bilaabato taariikhda guuritaanka ama taariikhda uu cinwaanka cusub uu noqdo mid joogto ah",
        "Whether the DSO has confirmed the SEVIS record was updated and any documentation that confirms the update": "Inay DSO-gu uu xaqiijiyay in diiwaanka SEVIS la cusboonaysiiyay iyo dukumenti kasta oo xaqiijinaya cusboonaysiinta",
        "Whether the J-1 sponsor has been notified within 10 days of any change in U.S. address, telephone, or email": "Inay kafiilka J-1 loo soo sheegay 10 maalmood gudahood isbeddel kasta oo cinwaanka U.S., taleefanka, ama iimaylka",
        "Whether the REAL ID expiration date may be tied to the I-94, the visa, or an I-797 or I-20 or DS-2019, and how renewal works after a status extension": "Inay taariikhda dhicitaanka REAL ID laga yaabo inay xidhnaado I-94, fiisaha, ama I-797 ama I-20 ama DS-2019, iyo sida cusboonaysiintu u shaqayso ka dib kordhinta xaaladda",
        "Whether the REAL ID expiration date may be tied to the underlying federal document": "Inay taariikhda dhicitaanka REAL ID laga yaabo inay xidhnaado dukumentiga federaalka ee hoosta yaal",
        "Whether the application asks for a lawful presence attestation": "Inay codsigu weydiinayo caddayn joogitaan sharci ah",
        "Whether the application asks for a lawful presence attestation and what document supports it": "Inay codsigu weydiinayo caddayn joogitaan sharci ah iyo dukumentiga taageeraya",
        "Whether the board accepts background-check results processed under your current status": "Inay guddigu aqbalo natiijooyinka baaritaanka asalka ee la baaray xaaladdaada hadda",
        "Whether the calendar-year count of days under the Substantial Presence Test meets the federal threshold for the current year": "Inay tirinta maalmaha sannadka jadwalka hoos imanaysa Substantial Presence Test ay buuxiso heerka federaalka ee sannadka hadda",
        "Whether the current nonimmigrant status appears on the current HealthCare.gov lawfully present list": "Inay xaaladda hadda ee aan-socdaal-doon ay ka muuqato liiska hadda ee HealthCare.gov ee joogitaanka sharciga",
        "Whether the current school DSO and the new school DSO have coordinated a SEVIS transfer release date": "Inay DSO-ga dugsiga hadda iyo DSO-ga dugsiga cusub ay isku duweeyeen taariikhda sii-deynta u wareejinta SEVIS",
        "Whether the current status is within a recognized federal eligibility group for Medicare or Medicaid": "Inay xaaladda hadda ay ku jirto koox u qalmitaan federaal oo la aqoonsado ee Medicare ama Medicaid",
        "Whether the destination Board of Nursing requires an SSN at application, and whether an ITIN, attestation, or affidavit is accepted as an alternative": "Inay Guddiga Kalkaalisada ee aad u socotid uu u baahan yahay SSN codsiga, iyo inay ITIN, caddayn, ama dhaariyo qoraal ah loo aqbalo bedel ahaan",
        "Whether the destination DMV requires original documents and current address proofs, and whether copies or translations are accepted": "Inay DMV-da aad u socotid uu u baahan yahay dukumentiyo asal ah iyo caddaymaha cinwaanka hadda, iyo inay nuqulada ama turjumaadaha la aqbalayo",
        "Whether the destination address is being reported to the DSO or J-1 sponsor within 10 days of the move": "Inay cinwaanka aad u socotid u sheegayo DSO-ga ama kafiilka J-1 10 maalmood gudahood guuritaanka",
        "Whether the destination state accepts an ITIN where an SSN is requested on its return": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu aqbalo ITIN halka SSN laga codsado soo celinta",
        "Whether the destination state accepts an ITIN where an SSN is requested on its return, and whether a separate state tax ID is offered": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu aqbalo ITIN halka SSN laga codsado soo celinta, iyo inay aqoonsi canshuur gobol oo gooni ah la bixinayo",
        "Whether the destination state conforms to federal income tax treaty exclusions for nonresident aliens, or taxes that income at the state level": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu raaco marka laga reebo heshiiska canshuurta dakhliga federaalka ee nonresident aliens, ama uu canshuuriyo dakhligaas heerka gobolka",
        "Whether the destination state considers you a resident": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid kuu tixgalinayo degane",
        "Whether the destination state defines residency by domicile, by days of physical presence, or by a combination": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu degenaanshaha ku qeexo domicile-ka, maalmaha joogitaanka jirka, ama isku-darka",
        "Whether the destination state has a tuition-equity or high-school-attendance provision that could apply, and what documentation it requires": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu leeyahay qodob sinaanta kharashka waxbarashada ama ka qaybgalka dugsiga sare oo khusayn karta, iyo dukumentiyada uu uga baahan yahay",
        "Whether the destination state has a tuition-equity policy that may apply, and what documentation it requires": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu leeyahay siyaasad sinaanta kharashka waxbarashada laga yaabo inay khusayso, iyo dukumentiyadeeda loo baahan yahay",
        "Whether the destination state has additional reporting or filling rules": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu leeyahay qawaaniin warbixin ama buuxin oo dheeri ah",
        "Whether the destination state has different tax withholding forms": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu leeyahay foomamka hayidda canshuurta oo kala duwan",
        "Whether the destination state has elected the CHIPRA option to cover lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals without a federal waiting period": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu doortay ikhtiyaarka CHIPRA si uu u daboolo carruurta iyo dadka uurka leh ee sida sharci ah u degan iyada oon muddada sugitaanka federaalka la sugin",
        "Whether the destination state imposes a minimum remaining stay on the I-94 before issuing a credential": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu soo rogo joogitaan ugu yar oo hadhsan I-94 ka hor inta uusan bixinin aqoonsi",
        "Whether the destination state offers a separate marked credential for some non-citizen applicants": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu bixinayo aqoonsi calaamadeysan oo gaar ah codsadayaasha qaar ka mid ah aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn",
        "Whether the destination state offers any state-funded coverage for non-citizens who do not qualify for federal Medicaid": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu bixiyo caymis lacag gobol oo aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee aan u qalmin Medicaid federaal",
        "Whether the destination state offers any state-funded coverage for people not eligible for the federal marketplace": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu bixiyo caymis lacag-gobol leh dadka aan u qalmin suuqa federaalka",
        "Whether the destination state offers any voting that is open to non-citizens (for example, certain local elections), and how that may interact with federal voter rolls": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu bixinayo codbixin furan aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn (tusaale, doorashooyinka deegaanka qaarkood), iyo sida ay taas ula falgashan karto liisaska codbixiyaasha federaalka",
        "Whether the destination state operates a non-FAFSA aid application for students who cannot file a FAFSA": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu maamulayo codsi kaalmo aan-FAFSA-ahayn ardayda aan filiga karin FAFSA",
        "Whether the destination state operates state-funded SNAP, TANF, or cash-assistance programs that may apply during the federal waiting period": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu maamulayo barnaamijyada SNAP, TANF, ama kaalmada lacagta lacag-gobol leh oo laga yaabo inay khusayaan inta lagu jiro muddada sugitaanka federaalka",
        "Whether the destination state participates in the Nurse Licensure Compact and how that interacts with non-citizen documentation": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu ka qaybqaado Nurse Licensure Compact iyo sida ay taas ula falgasho dukumentiyada aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn",
        "Whether the destination state recognizes your specific visa category as one that may establish a domicile for tuition purposes": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu aqoonsado qaybta fiisahaaga gaarka ah inay tahay mid laga yaabo inay aasaaso domicile ujeeddooyinka kharashka waxbarashada",
        "Whether the destination state requires a Social Security card or an SSA ineligibility letter, and how the visa category interacts with SSN issuance timing": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu u baahan yahay kaadhka Social Security ama warqadda u-qalmi-la'aanta SSA, iyo sida qaybta fiisuhu uu ula falgasho wakhtiga bixinta SSN",
        "Whether the destination state uses HealthCare.gov or runs its own state-based marketplace": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu isticmaasho HealthCare.gov ama uu maamulo suuqiisa gobol",
        "Whether the destination state uses HealthCare.gov or runs its own state-based marketplace with separate documentation rules": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu isticmaalo HealthCare.gov ama uu maamulo suuqiisa gobol oo leh qawaaniin dukumenti oo gooni ah",
        "Whether the destination state uses the CHIPRA/ICHIA option to remove the waiting period for children, pregnant people, or both": "Inay gobolka aad u socotid uu isticmaalo ikhtiyaarka CHIPRA/ICHIA si looga saaro muddada sugitaanka carruurta, dadka uurka leh, ama labadaba",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV asks all applicants about voter registration, including non-citizens": "Inay DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid ay weydiiso dhammaan codsadayaasha diiwaangelinta codbixinta, oo ay ku jiraan aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV record reflects the new address on its own timeline": "Inay diiwaanka DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid uu muujinayo cinwaanka cusub jadwalkiisa gaarka ah",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV typically issues a credential to your visa category for the standard multi-year cycle or for a shortened cycle keyed to the I-94 or another federal document": "Inay DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid sida caadiga ah u siiso aqoonsi qaybta fiisahaaga ee wareegga-sano-badan ee caadiga ah ama wareeg gaaban oo ku xidhan I-94 ama dukumenti federaal kale",
        "Whether the destination-state DMV will issue a REAL ID to your specific visa category and which federal documents it requires": "Inay DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid uu siin doono REAL ID qaybta fiisaha aad gaarka ah iyo dukumentiyada federaalka uu uga baahan yahay",
        "Whether the destination-state board for your profession lists DACA recipients or lawful permanent residents in its documentation guidance": "Inay guddiga gobolka aad u socotid ee xirfaddaada uu ku liis garaynayo DACA-hayayaasha ama deganayaasha joogto ah ee sharciga ah hagidda dukumentiyada",
        "Whether the destination-state board for your profession lists nonimmigrant visa categories or OPT or academic training in its documentation guidance": "Inay guddiga gobolka aad u socotid ee xirfaddaada uu ku liis garaynayo qaybaha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah ama OPT ama tababar academic hagidda dukumentiyada",
        "Whether the destination-state license or ID application automatically initiates Selective Service registration": "Inay codsiga shatiga ama aqoonsiga ee gobolka aad u socotid si toos ah u bilaabayo diiwaangelinta Selective Service",
        "Whether the employer is filing a new LCA and an amended Form I-129 before or shortly after the worker reports to the new worksite": "Inay shaqaalaha bixiya shaqadu uu gudbinayo LCA cusub iyo Foomka I-129 ee la beddelay ka hor ama wax yar ka dib markuu shaqaaluhu u tago goobta shaqo ee cusub",
        "Whether the employer or petitioner is filing an amended Form I-129 before the worker reports to the new location": "Inay shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada ama codsaduhu uu gudbinayo Foomka I-129 ee la beddelay ka hor inta uu shaqaaluhu u tago goobta cusub",
        "Whether the exception covers a specific person depends on age, current status, and continuity of valid nonimmigrant status, and a later transition to LPR or naturalization can revive a registration question relevant to federal benefits and naturalization.": "Inay marka laga reebay uu daboolayo qof gaar ah waxay ku xirantahay da'da, xaaladda hadda, iyo sii-socoshada xaaladda aan-socdaal-doon ah ee ansax ah, u kala-guurka dambe ee LPR ama dhalashada ayaa soo nooleyn karta su'aal diiwaangelin oo khusaysa manaafacaadka federaalka iyo dhalashada.",
        "Whether the existing LCA needs to be posted at the new worksite for the required period": "Inay LCA-da hadda jirta loo baahan yahay in lagu daabaco goobta shaqada ee cusub muddada loo baahan yahay",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 address change has been filed within 10 days of the residential move": "Inay isbeddelka cinwaanka AR-11 ee federaalka lagu gudbiyay 10 maalmood gudahood guuritaanka degenaanshaha",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 filing is also needed as a separate step": "Inay gudbinta AR-11 ee federaalka sidoo kale loo baahan yahay tallaabo gooni ah",
        "Whether the federal AR-11 filing is also needed in addition to sponsor notification": "Inay gudbinta AR-11 ee federaalka sidoo kale loo baahan yahay ka sokow ogeysiiska kafiilka",
        "Whether the institution you plan to attend sets its own classification rules in addition to any state policy": "Inay hay'adda aad qorshaynayso inaad gasho ay dejiso qawaaniintiisa gaarka ah ee kala saaridda ka sokow siyaasad kasta oo gobol",
        "Whether the item is regulated by state law": "Inay cinwaanka uu nidaamiyo sharciga gobolka",
        "Whether the license expiration is tied to the federal document expiration date": "Inay dhicitaanka shatigu uu xidhan yahay taariikhda dhicitaanka dukumentiga federaalka",
        "Whether the medication is a controlled substance under federal or state law": "Inay dawadu tahay walax la nidaamiyo sharciga federaalka ama gobolka",
        "Whether the move triggers a special enrollment period and the documentation needed to verify status": "Inay u guuritaanku uu kicinayo muddada isdiiwaangelinta gaarka ah iyo dukumentiyada loo baahan yahay xaqiijinta xaaladda",
        "Whether the new employer's payroll setup reflects the exemption": "Inay habka mushaharka ee shaqaalaha bixiya shaqo cusubku uu muujinayo marka laga reebay",
        "Whether the new physical and mailing address has been entered in the SEVP Portal or reported to the DSO within 10 days": "Inay cinwaanka cusub ee jirka iyo boostada lagu galiyay SEVP Portal ama loo sheegay DSO-ga 10 maalmood gudahood",
        "Whether the new worksite falls inside the MSA or area of intended employment listed on the current LCA": "Inay goobta shaqada ee cusub ku dhacayso gudaha MSA ama aagga shaqada loogu talagalay ee ku qoran LCA-da hadda",
        "Whether the new worksite is inside the same MSA or area of intended employment as the current LCA, or in a new MSA": "Inay goobta shaqo ee cusub ay ku jirto MSA isku mid ah ama aagga shaqada loogu talagalay sida LCA-da hadda, ama MSA cusub",
        "Whether the online change-of-address tool in a USCIS online account is the right path, or whether a paper Form AR-11 is needed": "Inay qalabka cinwaan-bedelka onlaynka ee xisaabta onlaynka USCIS uu yahay jidka saxda ah, ama inay Foomka AR-11 warqad loo baahan yahay",
        "Whether the original L-1 or O-1 petition listed a specific worksite, employer location, or itinerary that the move changes": "Inay codsiga asalka ah ee L-1 ama O-1 uu lifaaqay goob shaqo oo gaar ah, goobta shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, ama jadwal uu guuritaanku bedelo",
        "Whether the person is within the age range to which the federal requirement may apply": "Inay qofku ku jiro da'da ay shuruudda federaalku khusayn karto",
        "Whether the program start date and on-campus reporting deadline at the new school have been confirmed": "Inay taariikhda bilaabista barnaamijka iyo kama dambaysta warbixinta kambaska dugsiga cusub la xaqiijiyay",
        "Whether the tax year of the move includes both nonresident and resident periods for federal tax purposes": "Inay sannadka canshuurta ee guuritaanku uu ku jiro labadaba muddooyinka nonresident iyo resident ujeeddooyinka canshuurta federaalka",
        "Whether the waiting period applies, whether a state option removes it for children or pregnancy, and which documents are accepted can change between origin and destination states and affect coverage continuity.": "Inay muddada sugitaanku khusayso, inay ikhtiyaarka gobolku ka saaro carruurta ama uurka, iyo dukumentiyada la aqbalo way isbeddeli karaan u dhaxeeyo gobollada aad ka soo kacaysid iyo aad u socotid waxayna saamayn ku yeelan karaan sii-socoshada caymiska.",
        "Whether the worker still meets the IRS conditions for the F-1, J-1, M-1, or Q FICA exemption (status type, primary purpose, and federal tax residency)": "Inay shaqaaluhu weli buuxiyo shuruudaha IRS ee marka laga reebay FICA ee F-1, J-1, M-1, ama Q (nooca xaaladda, ujeeddada aasaasiga ah, iyo degenaanshaha canshuurta federaalka)",
        "Whether their current nonimmigrant status is on the list described by the Selective Service System as covered by the exception": "Inay xaaladdooda hadda ee aan-socdaal-doon ah ay ku jirto liiska uu Nidaamka Selective Service ku qeexay sida la daboolay marka laga reebo",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney about how AR-11 interacts with a specific status": "Inay tahay in la tashado qareen socdaal oo shati haysta oo ku saabsan sida AR-11 ula falgasho xaalad gaar ah",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney about how registration history may interact with later filings": "Inay tahay in la tashado qareen socdaal oo shati haysta oo ku saabsan sida taariikhda diiwaangelinta ay ula falgashan karto gudbinno dambe",
        "Whether to consult a licensed immigration attorney before submitting status documentation to the marketplace": "Inay tahay in la tashado qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta aan loo gudbin dukumentiyada xaaladda suuqa",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer familiar with non-citizen federal tax issues before relying on a particular residency conclusion": "Inay tahay in la tashado diyaariye canshuur oo yaqaan arrimaha canshuurta federaalka ee aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ka hor inta aan lagu tiirsanaan gunaanad degenaansho gaar ah",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer or the employer's payroll team to verify FICA setup after the move": "Inay tahay in la tashado diyaariye canshuur ama kooxda mushaharka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada si loo hubiyo dejinta FICA ka dib guuritaanka",
        "Whether to consult a tax preparer who handles dual-status filings": "Inay tahay in la tashado diyaariye canshuur oo qabta gudbinno xaalad labanlaha ah",
        "Whether to consult employer counsel and a licensed immigration attorney before the worker starts at the new location": "Inay tahay in la tashado qareenka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada iyo qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta uu shaqaaluhu ka bilaabin goobta cusub",
        "Whether to consult employer counsel before relying on intra-MSA treatment": "Inay tahay in la tashado qareenka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada ka hor inta aan lagu tiirsanaan habkka gudaha-MSA-da",
        "Whether to consult petitioner counsel and a licensed immigration attorney before the worker starts at the new location": "Inay tahay in la tashado qareenka codsadaha iyo qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta uu shaqaaluhu ka bilaabin goobta cusub",
        "Whether to consult the DSO and a licensed immigration attorney before changing employers around an interstate move": "Inay tahay in la tashado DSO-ga iyo qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta aan la bedelin shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada agagaarka u guuritaanka gobol-dhaafka ah",
        "Whether to consult the DSO and a licensed immigration attorney before making decisions that affect the transfer timeline": "Inay tahay in la tashado DSO-ga iyo qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta aan la qaadin go'aano saamayn ku leh wakhtiga u wareejinta",
        "Whether to consult the destination-state Medicaid agency for current eligibility categories": "Inay tahay in la tashado hay'adda Medicaid ee gobolka aad u socotid qaybaha u qalmitaanka hadda",
        "Whether to consult the responsible officer or alternate responsible officer at the sponsor and a licensed immigration attorney for category-specific guidance": "Inay tahay in la tashado sarkaalka mas'uulka ah ama sarkaalka kale ee mas'uulka kafiilka iyo qareen socdaal oo shati haysta hagid qayb-gaar ah",
        "Whether to keep dated confirmations of each address update in case a later filing relies on it": "Inay tahay in la hayo xaqiijinno taariikhaysan oo cusboonaysiin cinwaan kasta haddii gudbinta dambe ay ku tiirsanaato",
        "Whether translations or originals are required, and whether copies are accepted": "Inay turjumaaddo ama asal-ku-noole loo baahan yahay, iyo inay nuqulada la aqbalayo",
        "Whether you fall within a federal exception (for example, qualifying work history, certain humanitarian categories, or specific military-connected categories)": "Inaad ku jirto marka laga reebo federaal (tusaale, taariikhda shaqo ee u qalanta, qaybaha bani'aadannimo qaarkood, ama qaybaha gaarka ah ee la xiriira militariga)",
        "Whether you fall within a federal exception to the five-year waiting period (for example, certain humanitarian categories, military-connected status, or qualifying work history)": "Inaad ku jirto marka laga reebo federaal ee muddada sugitaanka shanta sano (tusaale, qaybaha bani'aadannimo qaarkood, xaaladda la xiriira militariga, ama taariikhda shaqo ee u qalanta)",
        "Whether you fall within the federal age range and category that must register": "Inaad ku jirto da'da iyo qaybta federaalka ee la baahan yahay in la diiwaangaliyo",
        "Whether you may owe a part-year return in the origin state and another in the destination state for the year of the move": "Inaad ku leedahay soo celin qayb-sano ah gobolka aad ka soo kacaysid iyo mid kale gobolka aad u socotid ee sannadka guuritaanka",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney about how Selective Service registration interacts with your specific status": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta oo ku saabsan sida diiwaangelinta Selective Service ula falgashato xaaladdaada gaarka ah",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before signing any voter-related paperwork": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta aadan saxiixin waraaq la xiriirta codbixinta",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before signing licensing attestations": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta aadan saxiixin caddaynta shatiga",
        "Whether you should consult a licensed immigration attorney before submitting any marketplace documents related to status": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta aadan gudbin dukumenti suuq oo la xiriira xaaladda",
        "Whether you should consult a tax preparer familiar with nonresident alien filers in the destination state": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato diyaariye canshuur oo yaqaan filerada nonresident alien ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Whether you should consult a tax preparer who is familiar with non-citizen filers in the destination state": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato diyaariye canshuur oo yaqaan filerada aan-muwaadiniinta-ahayn ee gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Whether you should consult both the board and a licensed immigration attorney before signing licensing attestations": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato labadaba guddiga iyo qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor inta aadan saxiixin caddaynta shatiga",
        "Whether you should consult both the financial-aid office and a licensed immigration attorney about how your status documentation will be used": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato labadaba xafiiska kaalmada maaliyadeed iyo qareen socdaal oo shati haysta oo ku saabsan sida dukumentiyada xaaladdaada loo isticmaali doono",
        "Whether you should consult both the registrar and a licensed immigration attorney about how your documentation may interact with classification": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato labadaba diiwaangeluhu iyo qareen socdaal oo shati haysta oo ku saabsan sida dukumentiyadaadu ay ula falgashan karaan kala saaridda",
        "Whether you should consult the registrar, your designated school official, and a licensed immigration attorney about how your documentation interacts with classification": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato diiwaangeluhu, sarkaalka dugsigaaga ee loo magacaabay, iyo qareen socdaal oo shati haysta oo ku saabsan sida dukumentiyadaadu ay ula falgasho kala saaridda",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney about timing a DMV renewal around a pending federal filing": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato sarkaalka dugsigaaga ee loo magacaabay, xidhiidhiyaha socdaalka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, ama qareen socdaal oo shati haysta oo ku saabsan wakhtiga cusboonaysiinta DMV-da agagaarka gudbin federaal oo sugaya",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney about timing renewals around an extension or change of status": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato sarkaalka dugsigaaga ee loo magacaabay, xidhiidhiyaha socdaalka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, ama qareen socdaal oo shati haysta oo ku saabsan wakhtiga cusboonaysiinta agagaarka kordhinta ama isbeddelka xaaladda",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney before applying": "Inay tahay inaad la tashato sarkaalka dugsigaaga ee loo magacaabay, xidhiidhiyaha socdaalka shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada, ama qareen socdaal oo shati haysta ka hor codsiga",
        "Whether you should speak with your prescriber or pharmacist": "Inay tahay inaad la hadasho dhakhtarka ku qoray dawada ama farmasi-yahankaaga",
        "Whether your EAD or permanent resident card is on the accepted-documents list": "Inay EAD-gaaga ama kaadhkaaga degenaha joogto ah uu ku jiro liiska dukumentiyada la aqbalo",
        "Whether your EAD or permanent resident card is on the board's current accepted-documents list": "Inay EAD-gaaga ama kaadhkaaga degenaha joogto ah uu ku jiro liiska hadda ee guddiga ee dukumentiyada la aqbalo",
        "Whether your current immigration status is on the marketplace's current 'lawfully present' list": "Inay xaaladdaada socdaalka hadda ku jirto liiska hadda ee suuqa ee 'joogitaanka sharciga'",
        "Whether your current license remains usable during a transition period": "Inay shatigaaga hadda jiraa weli la isticmaali karo muddo guuritaan",
        "Whether your current policy covers driving in the destination state": "Inay caymiskaaga hadda uu daboolayo wadidda baabuurka gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Whether your employer needs an updated address": "Inay shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada uu u baahan yahay cinwaan la cusboonaysiiyay",
        "Whether your employer needs updated state tax forms": "Inay shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada uu u baahan yahay foomamka canshuurta gobolka oo la cusboonaysiiyay",
        "Whether your employer's state tax withholding should be updated after the move": "Inay hayidda canshuurta gobolka ee shaqaalahaaga bixiya shaqo ay tahay in la cusboonaysiiyo ka dib guuritaanka",
        "Whether your employer's state tax withholding should be updated after the move and which form is used": "Inay hayidda canshuurta gobolka ee shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada ay tahay in la cusboonaysiiyo ka dib guuritaanka iyo foomka loo isticmaalo",
        "Whether your federal status document is on the destination-state DMV's accepted list for REAL ID": "Inay dukumentigaaga xaaladda federaalka uu ku jiro liiska la aqbalay ee DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid ee REAL ID",
        "Whether your health insurance network covers the destination state": "Inay shabakadda caymiskaaga caafimaad daboolayso gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Whether your insurer requires you to update your policy address": "Inay hay'adda caymiskaaga uu kaa baahan tahay inaad cusboonaysiiso cinwaanka caymiska",
        "Whether your license transfers via endorsement or reciprocity": "Inay shatigaaga u wareego iyada oo loo marayo aqoonsi ama isweydaarsi",
        "Whether your pharmacy can transfer the prescription": "Inay farmasigaaga uu u wareejin karo dawada dhakhtarku qoray",
        "Whether your specific school sets its own tuition-classification rules in addition to any state policy": "Inay dugsigaaga gaarka ahi uu dejiyo qawaaniintiisa gaarka ah ee kala saaridda kharashka waxbarashada ka sokow siyaasad gobol",
        "Whether your visa documents (passport with visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, EAD) are on the accepted-documents list": "Inay dukumentiyadaada fiisaha (baasaboor leh fiise, I-94, I-20 ama DS-2019, I-797, EAD) ay ku jiraan liiska dukumentiyada la aqbalo",
        "Which documents the destination state Medicaid agency uses to verify status": "Dukumentiyada uu hay'adda Medicaid ee gobolka aad u socotid u isticmaasho xaqiijinta xaaladda",
        "Which documents the destination-state agency uses to verify status": "Dukumentiyada uu hay'adda gobolka aad u socotid u isticmaasho xaqiijinta xaaladda",
        "Which factors apply (lease, employment, vehicle registration, voting, tax filing)": "Arrimaha khusayo (heshiis kirada, shaqo, diiwaangelinta baabuurka, codbixin, gudbinta canshuurta)",
        "Which federal immigration documents (for example, EAD, permanent resident card, USCIS notices) the destination-state DMV currently lists as acceptable": "Dukumentiyada socdaalka federaalka ee (tusaale, EAD, kaadhka degane joogto ah, ogeysiisyada USCIS) hadda lagu liis garaynayo inay la aqbalayo DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid",
        "Which federal immigration documents the destination-state DMV currently lists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (for example, passport with visa stamp, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, I-797, employer support letter)": "Dukumentiyada socdaalka federaalka ee uu hadda DMV-da gobolka aad u socotid ku liis garaynayo codsadayaasha fiisaha aan-socdaal-doon ah (tusaale, baasaboor leh shaambad fiise, I-94, I-20 ama DS-2019, I-797, warqadda taageero shaqaalaha bixiya shaqada)",
        "Which forms (1040, 1040-NR, and supporting statements) apply for a dual-status year": "Foomamka (1040, 1040-NR, iyo bayaannada taageerada) ay khusayaan sannad xaalad labanlaha ah",
        "Withholding the wrong state's taxes can lead to filing complications and unexpected balances.": "Hayidda canshuurta gobolka khaldan waxay horseedi kartaa dhibaatooyin gudbinta iyo hadhaagga aan la sii sheegin.",
        "Working in a licensed profession before completing the destination state's licensing process may have regulatory consequences.": "Ka shaqaynta xirfad shati leh ka hor inta aanad dhammaystirin habka shatiga ee gobolka aad u socotid waxay yeelan kartaa cawaaqib nidaameed.",
        "Worth knowing about. Usually administrative or low-stakes to verify.": "Wax la ogaado mudan. Inta badan waa maamul ama hubin yar oo khatar yar leh.",
        "YOUR CHECKLIST": "LIISKAAGA HUBINTA",
        "Your selections aren't saved or shared. The checklist is generated locally.": "Doorashooyinkaagu lama keydiyo lamana wadaago. Liiska hubintu waxa lagu abuuraa qalabkaaga.",
        "eCFR 22 CFR 62.13 Notification Requirements": "eCFR 22 CFR 62.13 Shuruudaha Ogeysiiska",
        "eCFR 22 CFR Part 62 Exchange Visitor Program": "eCFR 22 CFR Qaybta 62 Exchange Visitor Program",
        "eCFR Part 62 covers J-1 Exchange Visitor Program regulations. Curl returned 200 but with an unblock.federalregister.gov redirect, consistent with an anti-bot challenge on a long-standing .gov resource; the canonical eCFR URL still resolves in a browser.": "eCFR Qaybta 62 waxay dabooshay qawaaniinta J-1 Exchange Visitor Program. Curl wuxuu soo celiyay 200 laakiin oo leh wareejin unblock.federalregister.gov, taas oo la mid ah caqabad ka-hortagga botka ee kheyraad .gov ah; URL-ka eCFR ee caanka ah ayaa wali ku shaqaynaya browser.",
        "eCFR section that describes J-1 sponsor and exchange-visitor notification obligations. Same eCFR anti-bot redirect observed.": "Qaybta eCFR oo qeexaysa waajibaadyada ogeysiiska kafiilka J-1 iyo booqdeyaasha is-weydaarsiga. Isla wareejinta ka-hortagga botka ee eCFR ayaa la arkay.",
    ]
    static let farsi: [String: String] = [:]
